\id 1CO -Boga Translation Project
\toc3 1 Kr
\toc1 TƏRKA THLIN YARAT ƊELWERA BULUS KƏ MBƏƊA KORINTIYAWECHA
\toc2 1 KORINTIYAWECHA
\toc1 TƏRKA THLIN YARAT ƊELWERA BULUS KƏ MBƏƊA KORINTIYAWECHA
\mt2 TƏRKA THLIN YARAT ƊELWERA BULUS KƏ MBƏƊA
\mt1 KORINTIYAWECHA
\c 1
\s1 Ndat Ənna
\p 
\v 1 Yarat ɗelwertiya ɓakna mbǝɗengna njang Bulus, at Fara tǝ ngǝmtǝ'en kǝ naka lǝthlǝnda Yǝso Kǝrǝsti. Paɗ yaraki ɗelwertiya tǝ hwanmanǝm Sastanis.
\v 2 Nakani yarat ɗelwertiya kǝ ɓǝɗa fa tǝrmbanda Fara hur Korinti, tǝ mbǝɗa fichile taɗtǝ fichihar a hur Yǝso Kǝrǝsti, atfichǝ kandǝ kǝnandǝ chiɗchiɗ, nat tǝ fichile chika ayi la ak thlǝm Lǝmwaɗengnǝm Yǝso kǝrǝsti, Lǝmwaɗengnanda tǝ inǝm:
\v 3 Kafata tǝ yuyurchita mbǝɗa Shinnǝm Fara tǝ Lǝmwaɗengnǝm, Yǝso Kǝrǝsti kǝ mbǝɗengnuni.
\s1 Sǝt Usoko
\p 
\v 4 Kǝnding la naki sandǝ Farǝ usoko kǝthlǝm kunang, kǝthlǝm kafaɗi Farǝ fǝrandǝna kuni tǝ mbǝɗa Kǝrǝsti Yǝso.
\v 5 Chika tǝ mba yeni fǝraɗǝ hurmichita kuni a fat'en, hur shuwunchengnuni tǝ sǝn'ǝn paɗ nat,
\v 6 kǝthlǝm ɓeɗ ficha mbǝsandǝ sheta engnani kǝ ɗar Kǝrǝsti a hurnuni.
\v 7 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn ɓahwuni chika witǝ fǝr shemeɗ muwa, nda i natuni ɗǝf hwanita ɓata Lǝmwaɗengnǝm Yǝso Kǝrǝsti;
\v 8 Le na kǝskunihar tǝ alchita kǝ mweshitkǝn, kǝthlǝm kǝ sokuni nga fa chithansarǝhiwa a farǝ ɓata Lǝmwaɗengnǝm Yǝso Kǝrǝsti.
\v 9 Fara, lǝ nǝhɗandǝ ɗǝfshundǝhi mǝlan ak kuni kǝnuni ɓweet tǝ hwe'en Yǝso Kǝrǝsti Lǝmwandengnǝm.
\s1 Sakchǝhi a Hur fa Tǝrmbanda
\p 
\v 10 Hwanaɗi kuni, hwanmancha, a hur thlǝm Lǝmwaɗengnǝm Yǝso Kǝrǝsti ndatwa: "Natuni kǝ ngǝmuni tǝ ndani mǝni saktǝhi sa hurnuniwa, kǝ humangnguni inda kǝna yarengnuni ǝrta, hanndǝkikechengnuni paɗ ǝrta."
\v 11 Hwanmanchina mbu'i nofchi hura'a Kuluwi yu, ndatwa mbatsa thlerǝnuni.
\v 12 I nati yarǝ ndatwa, chika wuna hurnuni mǝla mbu ǝn somǝn, ndatwa: "Njang i Bulus, "Yuna ndatwa, "Njang i Afolos, "Yunǝ paɗwa, "Njang i Kefas, "Yunǝwa" Njang i Kǝrǝsti."
\v 13 Awi a shek Kǝrǝsti hiwa? Ndu Bulus kukwandǝfichihi kǝthlǝm kunang? Ndu sang fichi baptisma kuni hur thlǝm Bulus?
\v 14 Saɗi Farǝ usoko sawi baptisma yuna hurnuniwa, nda Kirisbus tǝ Gayus ndak sandi kanda,
\v 15 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn yunǝsǝ na ndatwa sangfichi baptisma hur Thlǝmnǝwa.
\v 16 Kit a saɗi baptisma nofchi hura'a Istifanus. Ɗifitǝ ndǝkǝn kuɗukwi ndu saɗi baptisma yunǝ paɗwa.
\v 17 Thlǝnu Kǝrǝsti njiwa kǝ si baptisma wa, paɗ kǝ ɓassi laulawata nga tǝ mbǝr sǝn'ǝna nifǝwa, kǝthlǝm mǝ sǝɓa fichi alchit palita Kǝrǝsti ɗǝwa.
\s1 Kǝrǝsti Alchita Fara tǝ Sǝn'ǝn'en
\p 
\v 18 Pathla palita ɓomchita mbǝɗa fichile naka mba thlǝrǝttaɗi, paɗ kǝ mbǝɗengnani kanang ti hǝrǝkka alchita Fara.
\v 19 Kǝthlǝm yara fichǝhi ndatwa:
\q1 "Ni wuwelandǝ sǝn'ǝna lǝ sǝnda ɗi,
\q2 kǝ sayi ɗathla lǝ ɗathlaɗi kǝ'ǝn pofǝn."
\p 
\v 20 A ai fa ɗathla? A ai fa sǝn'icha? A ai fa halǝ'inda kisshi'iya? A chawu Fara kishwa ɗathla kisshi'iya ɓomchitwowa?
\v 21 Sokkǝn a hur ɗathla Fara, sǝnu kisshitǝ Farǝ tǝ mbanda ɗathlǝ'enwa, mbǝnangna Farǝ fa kǝ hǝrkaǝn fichile fǝrkǝkit, tǝ mbǝɗa ɓomchit ɓassǝ laulawatkǝn.
\v 22 Keɗ Yahudawechǝ kǝ nandǝ sakǝtkǝn, Helenawecha naknda kat ɗathla,
\v 23 kanang kana ɓassǝ Kǝrǝsti kukwandǝ fichǝhi, i sokka ǝnat chithansarǝhi mbǝɗa Yahudawecha, ɓomchit paɗɗaa mbǝɗa punofcha,
\v 24 A nakǝn mbǝɗa fichile at Fara, ndu Yahudawecha ndu Helenawecha nat hwaa, Kǝrǝsti alchita Fara tǝ ɗathla Fara.
\v 25 Kǝthlǝm i tǝrtǝ fichǝwa shiɗ Farǝ ɓomchita, sheraɗa ɗathla nifa, paɗ ɓah alchita Fara, sheraɗa alchita nifa.
\v 26 Hwanmancha yaramǝn naɗengnunihi fari at fichi kuni. Nga terchǝnuni nak tǝ sǝn'ǝn witǝ i nifǝwa; nga terchin nak tǝ mwandǝwa, paɗ nga terchin ngǝttǝ fichǝ nda kuturchǝwa.
\v 27 Farǝ taɗkǝn i har naka ɓomchita kish, kǝthlǝm kǝ harangfat fa ɗathla, taɗkǝ Farǝ i nak ɓukɓukka hur kisshita kǝ harangfat fa alchita.
\v 28 Taɗkǝ Farǝ ǝnat kuɓanda fata tǝ i njirtǝ kisshita nat tǝ ichi nguchǝksi kǝthlǝm i la nat nofcha tǝrtǝwa ndiichin kǝ saǝn nga'ǝnwa.
\v 29 Nat ichiniyu, sǝkǝn kǝthlǝm mǝ tǝri nifǝ tǝ hwasa'inwa ǝn nakǝn a mbanitǝ Farǝ wa.
\v 30 Farǝ sǝka natuni hur Yǝso Kǝrǝsti, le sokka ɗathlengnǝmma mbǝɗa Fara, mǝllan sokka fǝrkit engnǝm, chiɗchiɗchita tǝ hǝrǝktengnǝm.
\v 31 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn nda i natna hur yaratkǝn: "Chikawun na thla'a'ndǝ inda kǝ thla'angka hur Lǝmwanda."
\c 2
\s1 Ɓassǝ Pathla Kǝrǝsti le Kukwandǝficha
\p 
\v 1 Hwanmancha, ma ɓeɗi mbǝɗengnuni, ɓuwi kǝthlǝm kǝ mbwa'aikuni i naka ɓuɓweeta Fara, tǝ mbǝr shunda ndu tǝ sǝn'ǝnwa.
\v 2 Kǝthlǝm tepi tirihur yahwisa sǝn'ǝn somǝn naki tǝ kuniwa, Yǝso Kǝrǝsti ndak, le kukwandǝfichǝhi.
\v 3 Ɓaki mbǝɗengnuni hur ɓah alchita tǝ lechita, paɗ tǝ saktatfǝ kaǝn.
\v 4 Lǝmfatsi ndu ɗathla hur shuɗengnǝ tǝ ɓassengnǝwa, tǝ cheɗndǝ alchita Shemeɗa,
\v 5 Kǝthlǝm fǝrkitchiɗengnuni mǝniɗa ɗar sǝn'ǝna nofchǝwa, kǝ naka ɗar alchita Fara.
\s1 Sǝn'ǝna Mbǝɗa Shemeɗa
\p 
\v 6 Chika tǝ kichu, la shuwunkani sǝn'ǝna kǝ mbǝɗa fichile mwanka hur fǝrkit, nga sǝn'ǝna kisshi'i nakǝnya ndu i kuturchi nakǝnya, fichile naka thlǝrǝttaɗǝwa.
\v 7 La nakani shuwun sǝn'ǝna Fara hur ɓuɓweetǝ yu, le naka hur ɓuɓweetǝ soh, sǝn'ǝni fǝrtǝ Farǝ soh kǝ tǝrka nathi kǝthlǝm mwaɗengnǝm.
\v 8 Hur kuturchi nakǝnya ngusǝ mbǝsang sǝn'ǝniyawa, mamuwa mbǝsanda, ma kukwawundǝ Lǝmwandǝ le nak mwanchinwa.
\v 9 Nda i nat yaratkǝna hur laulawatkǝn:
\q1 "I tahsandǝ Fara fichilesǝ la mbǝnkǝfatkǝn, tamu hwanita natwa, thlǝmatsǝ tamka sǝktǝwa, hanndǝkiketa nifǝsǝ tamka yarandǝhiwa."
\m 
\v 10 Kanang cheɗandǝ Fara kani tǝ mbǝɗa Shemeɗ'en. Shemeɗ la kaǝn chikamǝnat, chikamǝ naka hwengngǝchit icha Fara.
\v 11 Wuna hurnofcha sǝnkǝ yara nifa, manga Shemeɗi nifǝkǝn ti naka fi'enwa? Kichu paɗ nifǝsǝ sǝnkǝ yara Farǝ wa Shemeɗa Farǝ ndak.
\v 12 Thluwani shemeɗa kisshitǝwa, Shemeɗi ɓaka mbǝɗa Fara thlǝtani, kǝthlǝm kǝ sǝnani ichi fǝrandǝ Fara kani pofǝn.
\v 13 La mbwa'angani ichiya kuni, nga tǝ shuwunchǝ le sakandǝ fichaɗi tǝ mbǝɗa sǝn'ǝna nifǝwa tǝ shuwunchi sakandǝ fichaɗi tǝ Shemeɗa, tǝ mbu i naka kitchita shemeɗa a hur shunda Shemeɗa.
\v 14 Nifi nguchit Shemeɗa fi'en thlutǝ ichi ɓaka mbǝɗa Shemeɗa Farǝ wa, kǝthlǝm nakǝn kǝ ɓomchita mbǝɗ'en, paɗ ngu mbǝlla sǝn kandǝwa, kǝthlǝm tǝ mbǝɗa Shemeɗ la sǝntǝfichǝ kanda.
\v 15 Nifi nat Shemeɗsa fi'en la sǝnkǝ ichǝ nat, mǝllan tǝ indi'en nifǝsǝ na kikeɗandǝwa.
\q1 
\v 16 "Wun sǝnkǝ yara Lǝmwanda har natna sakandǝhar?"
\m Kanang yarengnani i Kǝrǝsti.
\c 3
\s1 Shikechǝ Tora Fara
\p 
\v 1 Hwanmancha, ngi mbǝlla mbwa'a' ǝna kuni nda nofchi naktǝ shemeɗa fǝwa, nda nofchi naka kisshita, paɗ nda hangwa'yarcha hur tǝrmbanda Kǝrǝsti.
\v 2 Yah fǝrandǝ kuni nga ɗǝsǝmtǝ kwaakwaawa, kǝthlǝm sǝkwunisa sǝm'ǝn kwaakwaa kwaɗǝnwa. Chika nakǝnya sǝkwunisǝwa,
\v 3 Kǝthlǝm paaya mwakuni hur fata. Makuna sǝrǝh ndani paɗ thlangǝtmisa thlerǝnuni, nga mwakuni hur fatwowa? Ɗǝsǝchengnuni nga nda tǝ fatwa?
\v 4 Kǝthlǝm ma ndeɗ yunǝwa, "Njang i Bulus", "Ndak yunǝwa", "Njang i Afolos", Nga tor fat natuni sǝtyuwa?
\p 
\v 5 Wun naka Afolos? Wun naka Bulus? Nga mafechǝwa fichile fǝrtuni kit tǝ mbǝɗengnanda, nda i fǝrandǝ Lǝmwanda tora chikawun engnanda?
\v 6 Njang hǝfkǝ hanwǝtǝkǝn, thlǝrkǝ Afolos amsǝ, paɗ Farǝ mwanangnga.
\v 7 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn, lǝ hǝfkǝn tǝ le thlǝrkǝ amsi nga naknda mi ǝnwa, Farǝ ndak mǝllanti la mwanangnga.
\v 8 Lǝ hǝfkǝn tǝ lǝ thlǝr amkǝnsi nakndǝ ǝrta, chika wuna hurnanda nakficha kwanandǝ keeke tǝ tor'en.
\v 9 Kǝthlǝm kanang shikechǝ fa torcha Fara, kunang hita Fara, tinda Fara.
\p 
\v 10 Tǝ mbǝɗa kafaɗi fǝritǝ Fara, a ɗǝfi thlorǝ tindǝhi kǝ lǝ mbǝr tinda, ɓakyuna nata chekandǝ tinkǝn kǝ ɗarkǝn. Chikawuni kǝ sǝn hǝɓaakǝ tǝ witǝ tindǝ'en.
\v 11 Kǝthlǝm nifǝsǝ na ɗǝf thlorǝ tinda kǝ pǝɗangka le hi ɗǝftǝ fichǝhiwa, le naka Yǝso Kǝrǝsti.
\v 12 Nakǝnya ma tin yunǝ kǝ ɗar thlorǝ tinkǝn tǝ zinariya, ndu tǝ azurfa, ndu tǝ ngwichǝ ɗiichin, ndu tǝ afcha, ndu tǝ hwelaa, ndu tǝ kofcha,
\v 13 na tora chikawuna chetakish, kǝthlǝm fariniyu nan chetakissha ɗwaachitkǝn. Nak tora chikawuna chetakish tǝ hwata, hwatkǝn na kikeɗandǝ tora chikawuni.
\v 14 Ma tini sǝtficha kǝ ɗar thlorǝ tinkǝn hiriki iwaɗǝwa, le tinka nan thlǝt kǝnikǝn.
\v 15 Ma iɗ torkǝna ɗi, le tinka nan sat ɓahta, mǝllan tǝ indǝ'en nan hǝrǝkta nda nifi kuwurkǝ tǝ hur hwata.
\v 16 Awi sǝnwuniwa kunang tǝ inchengnuni naka kapat hura'a Farǝwa, paɗ nak Shemeɗa Farǝ tǝ sokta a hur hanndǝkikechengnuniwowa?
\v 17 Chikawun sǝɓang kapat hura'a Fara ɗi, na Fara sǝɓandaɗi; kǝthlǝm kapat hura'a Fara la nakǝn chiɗchiɗ, kunang naka kapat hura'a Farǝkǝn.
\p 
\v 18 Mǝ lǝmiɗuni inchengnuniwa. Ma yunǝsa hurnuni la yarkǝwa ɗathlchin a hur kisshi'i nakǝnya, kǝ saǝn fat'en nda ɓoma, kǝthlǝm kǝ sǝka lǝ ɗathla.
\v 19 Ɗathla kisshi'iya ɓomchita mbǝɗa Fara. Nda i natna hur yarat laulawatkǝn: "La kǝsaǝn fichile nak ɗathlchin a hur ɗathlengnanda."
\v 20 Tǝpaɗ: "A shin Lǝmwandǝwa yara fa ɗathlǝ nga ǝnwa."
\v 21 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn mǝ hupa nifǝ hǝsǝr tǝ nifǝwa. Kǝthlǝm chikamǝ nat innuni,
\v 22 ndu Bulus, ndu Afolos, ndu Kefas, ndu kisshita, ndu shisshingta, ndu mǝrtaɗi, ndu ichi nakǝnya, ndu ichi naka mban, nat innuni.
\v 23 Kunang paɗ i Kǝrǝsti, Kǝrǝsti paɗ i Fara.
\c 4
\s1 Fathlǝncha Kǝrǝsti
\p 
\v 1 Tǝkichu kemsi kǝ tǝruni kaniwa mafecha Kǝrǝsti, tǝ fichile ngǝmandǝ fichǝ kǝnandǝ tǝ ichi Farǝ naka ɓuɓweeta.
\v 2 Sokkǝn waat nifi malandǝ fichǝ ichahar kemsi kǝ mbǝsang fichǝ tǝ kitchita fa.
\v 3 A mbǝɗengna, hanhwan'ǝna kǝ nda fichǝwa kunang na sakimiya ndu mbǝt sakmiya chikawun nifa. Kitchitkǝn, njang mangi sakamiya faɗengniwa.
\v 4 A shini hur indengniwa naki yalfar, chika kichu ngu soktǝwa chiwi hansarǝhiwa. Lǝmwandǝ na kikeɗita.
\v 5 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn mǝ thlaɗuni sakmihi kǝ ɗar yunǝ pofǝn sa'u hanmunchikǝn kwaɗǝnwa; pwa'ama kǝ farǝ nat Lǝmwanda ɓata. Mǝllan na chandǝ ichi kissha ɓuɓweeta kǝ ɗwachitkǝn, kǝ cheɗin yara hanɗǝkikecha. A farǝniyu chikawun nan thlǝt hamtǝ'ena mbǝɗa Fara.
\p 
\v 6 Nakǝnya hwanmanchina, fǝrki sakǝt ichi natya kǝ faɗengnǝ tǝ Afolos kǝthlǝm kunang, kǝ sakuni ǝn tǝ mbǝɗengnani kǝ ɗar shuni ndatfichǝwa: "Mǝ mbǝraɗuni ihi yarandǝ fichihi hur laulawatkǝnwa." Mǝ thla'a yunǝ inda hurnuni kǝ mbǝrangka lehi kǝ ɗar yunǝwa.
\v 7 Wun sukǝ somǝnhi tǝ tahhǝt nofcha, mǝnakseku le thluchitu? Sokkǝnma tǝ thlǝna, mǝsǝk natu thla'a'ndǝ inda nda nga tǝ thlǝnǝwa?
\v 8 Tepi mbǝshuni nat ichi yahtuni! Tepi shokuni kǝ hurrumcha! Tepi shokuni kuturcha nga tǝ kanangwa! Mayahtengna kǝ sokuni ka kǝ kuturcha, kǝthlǝm kanang ma kǝ sokani kuturichitkǝn tǝ kuni.
\v 9 A naɗengna cheɗ Fara a ɗwachitkǝnwa, kanang fathlǝncha njirandǝ fichǝ kaniɗi kǝ ndukwatkǝn chika mi, nda nofchi thlandǝ fichǝ sakmi mǝrtaɗa kandǝsi, sangfichi kani kǝ ǝnat nata kisshita, tǝ mala'ika cha nat tǝ nofcha.
\v 10 Shokani kǝ ɓomcha Kǝrǝsti, kunang nakuni kǝ fa ɗathla hur Kǝrǝsti! Kanang fa kuɓanda fata, kunang nakuni kwaakwaa. Ficha natkuni tǝ kapatichita fa, kanang nga ǝnnakaniwa.
\v 11 Paa kǝ nakǝnya, nakani hur mita tǝ kusshimta, thlǝthlah njelecha naka fechengnani, ficha tǝpanda kani paɗ hurechengnanisǝwa.
\v 12 La sani tor kaǝn tǝ harchengnani. Ma erndǝ kani, ndǝfangani mbǝs'ǝnhara kanda; ma fǝrandǝ pwancha kani, kǝrǝskani.
\v 13 Ma sǝɓandǝ thlǝmchǝnaniɗi, la shunangani kandǝ tǝ kachita. Paaya sokkani nda chirǝfta kisshita, i nat chikawuna wuɗekta.
\v 14 Nga yaraki iya kǝthlǝm kǝ harangfat kuniwa, kǝ tahsayi kuni nda hwanchi yahti.
\v 15 Chikama sokkǝn fasakchengnunisǝ aru kumchitkum (10,000) a hur Kǝrǝsti, shinchǝnunisǝ terchinwa, kǝthlǝm njang naka shinnuni a hur Yǝso Kǝrǝsti tǝ mbǝɗa laulawata.
\v 16 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn nja hwanandǝ kuni kǝ sakuni nji.
\v 17 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn nja thlǝna Timoti kuni, hwe'engna le la mbǝntifatkǝn, le nak tǝ kachita a hur Lǝmwanda. Nan kuɗkanda kuni tǝ mbanda naɗengnǝhi a hur Yǝso Kǝrǝsti, nda i soktǝn keeke tǝ i sakandi ɗaɗi chika ayi hur chika yen mbǝt tǝrmbanda.
\v 18 Funa thla'a'ndǝ inda nda ngi ɓata mbǝɗengnuniwa
\v 19 Ma ngǝma Lǝmwanda ni ɓata mbǝɗengnuni chetchetya, kani tausandǝ alchiɗi mbǝstǝ fa thla'a'ndǝ iniyu kish tǝ shuwunchengnanda.
\v 20 Kǝthlǝm kuturichita Fara nga pathla shundǝwa pathla alchita.
\v 21 Mǝ yahtunisi? Kǝ ɓi mbǝɗengnuni tǝ kuɓwerǝwa, ndu hur mbǝnfata paɗ tǝ ngwallǝchit shemeɗa?
\c 5
\s1 Chamǝn Fǝlau tǝ Hwanmanda Kish
\p 
\v 1 Shikiwa fǝlawichitsa hurnuni, witǝ le tamuchit ficha sǝta chika hur fa sǝt tor ɗǝhhacha, yuna sok fǝlawichit tǝ nuh shinkǝn.
\v 2 Nakuni thla'a'ndǝ inda! Nga kwesh sǝtuni sǝɓhurwa? Chikawun sǝk iniyu kǝ chang ficha kissha hurnuni.
\v 3 Chika sokkǝn njangsǝ tǝ iɗengna mbǝnniyuwa, njang tǝ kuni hur hanɗǝkiketa. Tepi sakaɗi miya nifi sǝk witǝ iniyu, nda njangsa mbǝnniyu.
\v 4 Ma hwimunihi a hur thlǝm Lǝmwandǝ Yǝso njang tǝ kuni mbǝnniyu hur hanɗǝkiketa, paɗ alchita Lǝmwaɗengnǝm Yǝso mbǝnniyu,
\v 5 witǝ nifiniyu kǝ fǝranguni Sheɗan kǝthlǝm kǝ ɓǝllang ficha hur fata, mbah na shemeɗ'ena hǝrǝkta farǝ ɓata Lǝmwandǝ Yǝso.
\p 
\v 6 Thla'a'ndǝ inchengnuni ndǝɗuwa. Sǝnwuniwa, mehndǝ nguɗehkicha la huppang humbat tahasǝ njohmǝ wowa?
\v 7 Pa'amǝn ɗohhǝt mehniɗiyu fechengnuni, kǝ sokuni kǝ yuwa ɗokyeta le nguchit mehndǝsa fi'en, kǝthlǝm kittǝkǝn nakuni kichu. Kǝthlǝm teppa thlafichi ɓurat hwan shohraɗengnǝm i chohhǝm tala, mǝlan naka Kǝrǝsti.
\v 8 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn kǝsam chohhǝmtengnǝmhar nga tǝ ɗohhǝt mehndǝwa, mehǝn sǝɓfata tǝ ɓǝɓifata. Kǝla sǝm chohhǝmtengnǝm tǝ njohmi nguchit mehndǝsi, ndǝkǝn naka njohǝm kachita tǝ kitchita.
\v 9 Yaraɗi kunisa hur thlǝn yarat ɗelwer engna ndatwa mǝlla humiɗunihi tǝ fǝlauchiwa.
\v 10 Nga yarengnǝwa nofchi kisshi'iya naka fǝlauchiwa, tǝ fa yah'ichǝwa, tǝ fa ɗathlanda nofchifǝwa, tǝ fa sǝt tor ɗǝhhachǝwa. Kǝthlǝm ma nakǝn kichu sokkǝn waat kǝ chunikissha hur kisshita.
\v 11 Yarayi kunisi mǝ sokiɗuni tǝ chikawun la at fichiwa hwanmanda lǝ tǝrmbanda, ma la sǝkǝn fǝlawichita, ndu lǝ yah'icha, ndu lǝ mwanandǝ ɗǝhhacha, ndu lǝ erǝfata, ndu lǝ sat icha, ndu hara. Chika sǝm'ǝn mǝ sǝmiɗuni tǝ witǝ nofchiniyuwa.
\p 
\v 12 Mǝ kǝmikǝ tǝ sakamiya fichile nguchika hur tǝrmbanda? Nga fichile naka hur tǝrmbandǝ natuni sakamiya kandǝwa?
\v 13 Farǝ na sakamiya fichile nguchika hur tǝrmbanda: "Chamǝn ɓǝɓi nifa hurnuni."
\c 6
\s1 Mǝ ɗi Fafǝrkitta Muhhanhar Ndaniwa
\p 
\v 1 Ma yunǝsa hurnuni naka thlangǝtmi tǝ shekkǝn, mǝ ɗiɗa muhhanharkǝna mbǝɗa fa ɓah fǝrkitwa, nga kweshkǝn kǝ mbǝɗa fa fǝrkitwowa?
\v 2 Awi sǝnwuniwa fa fǝrkit na sakamiya kisshitǝwowa? Makunang na sakamiya kisshita, nguni mbǝla sakmi ichi top-topyawowa?
\v 3 A sǝnwuniwa kǝmnang na sakamiya Mala'ika chiwowa? Kana cheta ichi natma soktǝsa kisshi'iya!
\v 4 Ma witǝ muhhanhar chini engnunisiyu, mǝsǝk la ɗǝtuni tǝkǝna mbanitǝ fichile nguchika miya ǝna mbanitǝ fa tǝrmbanda?
\v 5 Mbuki iniyu kǝthlǝm kǝ harangfat kuni. Sokkǝnyawa yunǝsa hurnuni ǝrtǝ nak ɗathlchin na tahsandǝ thlerǝ fa fǝrkitaɗǝwa?
\v 6 Paɗ mǝsǝka hwanmanda la ɗǝtna muhhanhar hwanmankǝn a mbanitǝ fa ɓah fǝrkit?
\p 
\v 7 Muhhanhar ndani ti la muhtuniyu kǝttǝhi mbǝɗengnuni. Nga kweshkǝn kǝrǝstuni kǝ nuni ɓomchǝwowa? Mǝsǝk nguchituni kǝrǝstǝ kǝ ɗathlang ficha kuni fa?
\v 8 Kunang tǝ inchengnuni kuna ɗathlanda ndanifa kuna puppuk ndanihi, ta hwanmanchǝnuni la sanduni ichiniyu kanda.
\v 9 Awi sǝnwuniwa fa ɓah fǝrkit ngunda mbǝs yimta kutǝrichita Farǝwowa? Mǝ lǝmi fichi kuniwa, kǝthlǝm fa sǝɓtaɗaɗisi ndu fa sǝt torɗǝhhacha, ndu fa sǝt fǝlauwichita, ndu hishchǝ fa che fechengnanda, ndu hishchi fa mundǝ tǝ hishcha,
\v 10 ndu harcha, ndu fa yahta, ndu fa sat'icha, ndu fa erǝfata, ndu fa ɗathlanda nofchǝfa na mbǝs mbǝta hur kuturichita Farǝwa.
\v 11 Nak funengnuni kichuyu. Anakǝn sapa fichǝ kuniɗi, tahsafichǝ kuni, chafichǝ kuni kish a hur thlǝm Lǝmwandǝ Yǝso Kǝrǝsti, paɗ tǝ mbǝɗa Shemeɗa Farengnǝm.
\s1 Mwanamǝn Fara tǝ Fechengnuni
\p 
\v 12 "Chikamǝ ngǝmifichǝsi", Paɗ nga chikamǝ na kǝsitisǝwa. "Chikamǝ ngǝmifichǝsi", Chika kichu ngi sokta mafata chikamǝwa.
\v 13 "Ɗǝsǝmta kǝthlǝm hura, hur paɗ kǝthlǝm ɗǝsǝmta" Farǝ nan thlǝrtandǝ kandaɗǝ hwaa. Sufichǝ fata kǝthlǝm kǝ i fǝlawichitwa, kǝ naka i Lǝmwanda, Lǝmwandǝ paɗɗaa i fata.
\v 14 Thla'ang Farǝ Lǝmwanda hur mǝmatcha tǝ alchit'en, paɗ chika kǝm nan thla'a'ndǝ kǝm.
\v 15 Awi sǝnwuniwa fechengnuni njarǝ fata Kǝrǝsti tǝ indǝ'enwowa? Kemsǝ hachiya kǝ hari njarǝ fata Kǝrǝsti kǝ humayi kandǝ tǝ ɓǝɓimanda? Ngu tamtasǝtwa!
\v 16 Awi sǝnwuniwa nifi humangfat tǝ ɓǝɓimanda sokkǝndǝ fat ǝrtǝ tǝ ndǝwowa? Kǝthlǝm nda i nat yarat laulawatkǝn: "Chapndǝyu naknda soktǝ kǝ fat ǝrta."
\v 17 Le humang fat'enhi tǝ Lǝmwanda, sokkǝndǝ ǝrta hur shemeɗ tǝ ndi.
\v 18 Rahamna fǝlawichithar! Tahhǝt ɓǝɓichitfechi nat la sǝt nifa nakna kisshitǝ fat'en, paɗ le sǝk ɓǝɓichitfat tǝ mbanda fǝlawichita sǝkǝn ɓǝɓichitfat kǝ fa fat'en.
\v 19 Sǝnwuniwa fechengnuni kapat hura'a Fara le naktǝ Shemeɗ Chiɗchiɗ, naka a hanndǝkikechengnuni, le thlǝtuni ɓǝɗa Farǝ wowa? Nga nakuni tǝ alchit inchengnuniwa.
\v 20 Hikkǝ fichǝ kuni 'yang'yang. Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn mwanamǝn Farǝ tǝ fechengnuni.
\c 7
\s1 Hafata Sok Reta
\p 
\v 1 Nakǝnya kǝ ichi yaratuni ɗarkǝn, ndiichinsi hishnifǝ mǝ kahindǝ kanwa.
\v 2 Kǝthlǝm rahhanda fǝlawichit har, chikawun hishnifǝ kǝnan tǝ nuhkǝnsi, paɗ chikawun nuhnifǝ kǝnan tǝ sǝmahsi.
\v 3 Hishnifǝ kǝ fǝraǝn i kamkǝsa nuhkǝn i reta, nuhnifǝ paɗ kǝ fǝraǝn i kamkǝsa sǝmahha i reta.
\v 4 Kǝthlǝm nuhnifǝ alchit'ensǝ kǝ fa fat'en ichitkǝnwa, sǝmah ndak. Kichu paɗ sǝmah alchit'ensǝ kǝ fa fat'en ichitkǝnwa, nuhkǝn ndak.
\v 5 Mǝ njaɗuni ndaniwa, kǝnan tǝ ngǝmtengnuni hwaa, kǝ fari ɗǝftuni kǝthlǝm kǝna hur'inchengnuni hur hwanda kanuni ngǝr kǝmta, kǝthlǝm mǝ limi sheɗan kuni a ɗar ɓah kǝrǝstǝwa.
\v 6 Mbuki iya i kamkǝsi yarandǝhi, nga waatwa.
\v 7 Mamuwa nansǝta kǝna nofchǝ nat nda njang. Nakǝn chikawun hishnifa tǝ i fǝrandǝ Fara, leya tǝ witǝ i fǝrandǝn leyu paɗ tǝ witǝ ikǝn.
\p 
\v 8 Kǝ mbǝɗa fichile kahuchikkan tǝ ndǝllat nishcha fichile mǝrtǝ hishchengnandǝyu, a kǝllaɗengna keekesi kǝ soknda kahundǝ kanwa nda i nati.
\v 9 Ma ngunda mbǝla kǝs fechengnandǝ harwa, kǝ kahndǝ kan. Kweshkǝn kǝ kah nifǝ kan mǝni ita ɗi tǝ yahta.
\p 
\v 10 Kǝ mbǝɗa fichile kahkǝ kan nja ndandakuniwa, nga njangwa Lǝmwanda, ndatwa: "Nuhnifǝ mǝ sakindǝhi tǝ sǝmahwa."
\v 11 Ma ɓeɗa saktǝhi tǝndi, kǝ sokǝn kichuyu kǝnretsǝwa, manga kichuuwa kǝ tahsangndǝ thlerǝnandaɗi tǝ sǝmahha. Hishnifǝ paɗ mǝ sakiɗǝhi tǝ nuhkǝnwa.
\p 
\v 12 Kǝ mbǝɗa tahchikǝn paɗ ndakiwa: "Nga Lǝmwandǝ mbukǝwa." Ma yunǝ hwanmandǝsi nat nuhkǝn kǝla ɓahfǝrkit, ngim nuhnifǝkǝn kǝ sokǝn tǝndi, mǝ cheriɗǝndǝwa.
\v 13 Ma nuhnifǝsǝ nat sǝmah kǝ lǝ ɓahfǝrkit, ngim hisnifǝkǝn kǝ sokǝn tǝndi, mǝ cheriɗǝndǝwa.
\v 14 Kǝthlǝm hishnifǝ lǝ ɓahfǝrkit, tahsafichǝ chiɗchiɗ tǝ mbǝɗa nuhkǝn, paɗ nuhnifǝ lǝ ɓahfǝrkit, tahsafichaɗi chiɗchiɗ tǝ mbǝɗa sǝmahha. Manga kichuwa, hwechengnuni naknda nat tǝ putafa, nda i natǝn nakǝnya, nakndǝ chiɗchiɗ.
\p 
\v 15 Ma lǝ ɓahfǝrkittiyu yahkǝsa saktǝhi tǝ shetkǝn kǝnan kichu. A witǝ mbǝnniyu, hwanmandǝ kǝ nuhnifǝ ndu kǝ hishnifǝ nga waatsa sokkǝnwa. Kǝthlǝm Farǝ akǝn kǝm kǝ sok yuyurchit tǝ ndani.
\v 16 Sokǝn nuhnifa, shinnǝ ndu mbahya sokǝn na hǝrkandǝ sǝmatuuwa? Sokǝn hishnifa, shinnǝ ndu mbahya sokǝn na hǝrkandǝ nuhwuwa?
\s1 Witǝ Soki Yahtǝ Lǝmwandǝsǝ Kǝ Sokficha
\p 
\v 17 Chika witǝmǝ natma hurkǝn, chikawun kǝ sokka mbǝɗi ɗǝftǝ Lǝmwandǝndǝsi a nat'enhi, kǝ i at Farǝ ndi. Ndǝkǝn naka mbutengna kǝ mbǝɗa fafǝrkit nat.
\v 18 Wun taɓkǝ kǝ heshang ficha kǝ fari at fichǝndi? Mǝ sokiɗǝ kǝ lǝ ɓah heshiwa. Le heshuchika kǝ fari at fichǝndi, mǝ kiɗǝ heshiwa.
\v 19 Hesha tǝ ɓah hesha nga ǝn nakndǝwa, kuwur kussa Farǝ ndak naka ka'ǝna.
\v 20 Chikawun kǝ nan nda i natǝn kǝ fari at Fara ɗi.
\v 21 Naku kǝ mafat kana ficha atsǝwa? Mǝ kǝmu ǝnwa. Manu ɓǝs alchit iɗeku, sǝku tor tǝ mbayiniyu.
\v 22 Chikawun naka mafata kana Lǝmwanda atndi nakǝn kǝ nifi ɓǝske alchit iɗi'en a Lǝmwanda. Kichu paɗ le nguchika mafata kana ficha atndi nakǝn kǝ mafata Kǝrǝsti.
\v 23 Hikkǝ fichǝ kuni 'yang'yang mǝ niɗuni mafecha nofchǝwa.
\v 24 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn hwanmancha, chika hur witǝ sokmǝ atfichǝ chikawuni, kǝ sokǝn kichu nda i at Farǝndi, kǝnan tǝ Farǝ'en.
\s1 Fichǝle Kahuchikkan tǝ Fichile Mǝrtǝ Hishchengnanda
\p 
\v 25 Kǝ ɗar nishchi tamuchika kan, fǝriwu Lǝmwandǝ alchit shuɗe kǝ ɗarkǝnwa, paɗ naki fǝr i naka yarengna kǝ ɗar ndatwa njangti ngǝmitǝ fichǝsi a ɗar shisshetfata Lǝmwanda.
\v 26 Ma yarengna, kǝthlǝm ɓahhi natma hurkǝn nakǝnya, keekesi kǝ soknifǝ ichitkǝn nda i natǝn.
\v 27 A kehnikanwa? Mǝ kǝnǝ saktǝhiwa. Ma kahunikanwa, mǝ kǝnǝ nuhnifǝwa.
\v 28 Ma kehnikan sunǝ ɓǝɓichitfatwa, ma keh nuhhwekan sutǝ ɓǝɓichitfatwa. Fichile kahkǝkan nanda yimta ɓahtǝ somsomǝn a naɗihiya, njang tǝ yahhisǝ kǝnan paapa'a mbǝɗengnuni.
\p 
\v 29 I yarti hwanmancha, ndatwa hanmunchikǝn nguɗeh. Thlata nakǝnya kǝ mban fichile nat nishchengnandǝsi kǝ sokndǝ nda ngusengnandǝwa,
\v 30 Fa tita nda nga tǝnnda titwa, fichile naka mbǝnfata nda nga kanda mbǝnfatwa, fichile hikkǝ'ǝna kǝ nandǝ nda nga ichengnandǝ kǝ kǝsndǝharwa.
\v 31 Fichile naka sǝt tor tǝ ǝnat kisshita mǝ ɗǝfindǝ fatsǝwa. Kǝthlǝm kisshikǝn a naɗi nakǝnya, tǝ naka mbǝrtǝhi.
\p 
\v 32 Yahkisi kǝnuni cha'a hur thlahur i'nda. Nifi kahhuchikkan nak yarǝ'ena ɗar torcha Lǝmwanda, i natna sǝta kǝ tǝraǝn hura Lǝmwandǝhi.
\v 33 Le kahkǝkan nak yarǝ'ena nata ɗar ǝnat kisshita, mbayi natna sǝt kǝ tǝraǝn hura nuhkǝnhi.
\v 34 Paɗ shek hur'indǝ'enhi. Nuhnifǝ kahhuchikkan ndu nuhhweya nak yarǝ'ena ɗar torcha Lǝmwanda, la ɗǝfkǝn indǝ'en kaǝn kǝ mbǝɗa Lǝmwanda a hur fat tǝ shemeɗa. Nuhnifi kahkǝkan yarǝ'ena ɗar ǝnat kisshita, mbayi natna sǝt kǝ tǝraǝn hura sǝmahhi.
\v 35 Naki mbu ichiya kǝthlǝm kǝ kǝsangka kunisi, ngauwa kǝ ɓweshikuniwa, kǝthlǝm soktengnuni kǝnaka mbandǝ ndiichin mǝ saki yarengnunihi hur mwanandǝ Lǝmwandǝwa.
\p 
\v 36 Ma yaraa yunǝhiwa i natna sǝt kǝ ɗar nuhhwani ngwantǝn nga keekewa, a nakǝn hurrecha nuhhwankǝna mbǝrtǝhi paɗ a fat'en kemsǝ kǝ kahhǝnkan, kǝ sǝn kichu nda i yahtǝn. Nga tǝna sǝt ɓǝɓichitfatwa, kǝ kǝnangndǝ reta.
\v 37 Nifi thlarkǝ kit kǝ ɗar yara hanndǝkiketǝ'en ndatwa ǝnatkǝn nga waatwa paɗ nan mbǝlla kǝs indǝ'enhar, paɗ tira hanndǝkiketǝ'enwa ngu kahhandǝ nuhhwaniyuwa, mǝlan ma shiɗtǝ i nak keeke.
\v 38 Nifi kahhang nuhhwani ngwantǝn shiɗ keeke, paɗ nifi kahhauchik nuhhwani ngwantǝn shiɗtǝ i kamkǝsǝ kaǝn.
\p 
\v 39 Nuhnifǝ nakna kǝnda kǝ mbǝɗa sǝmahha ma tana mweehi tǝ shishingta. Ma mir sǝmahha, cheɗa kissha sahta kǝ kahhǝn chikawun yahtǝn, sokkǝn waat kǝ na hishnifǝkǝna i Lǝmwanda.
\v 40 A thlandǝ shuɗengnǝhi, nan nat tǝ mbǝnfat kaǝn manan soktǝ ichitkǝn nda i natǝn. Paɗ la sikǝnfǝ Shemeɗa Farengnǝsi.
\c 8
\s1 Ɗǝsǝmi Fǝrandǝ Ficha Ɗǝhhacha
\p 
\v 1 Nakǝnya pathlǝ ɗǝsǝmi fǝrandǝ ficha ɗǝhhacha: "Shinǝmwa nattǝm sǝɗengnǝmsi." Sǝndǝ la ɓakǝn tǝ thla'inda, mbǝnfata la tinaǝn.
\v 2 Ma tiryunǝwa shintǝ'ǝna, paaya sǝnu nda i kamkǝsi kǝ sǝnǝnwa.
\v 3 Ma yuna mbǝnfat Fara, shin Farǝ ndi.
\p 
\v 4 Pathlǝ sǝm ɗǝsǝmi fǝrandǝ ficha ɗǝhhacha: "A shinǝmwa ɗǝhhata nga ǝnnakǝnna kisshitǝwa paɗ Farǝsǝ somǝnwa ǝrta."
\v 5 Chika sokkǝnwa funisǝ la atfichǝwa farǝcha a Afshi ndu kisshita (nda i nat, "farǝchǝsǝ" ka'ǝn "shinchǝsǝ" paɗ kaǝn),
\v 6 Chika kichu a mbǝɗengnǝm Farǝ ǝrta, le naka Shinda, ichi natya ɓakna mbǝɗ'en, naɗengnǝmhi kǝthlǝm mǝlan. Lǝmwandǝsi ǝrta Yǝso Kǝrǝsti, tǝ mbǝɗ'en chet ichi kish natya, kǝmnang paɗ naɗengnǝmhi tǝ mbǝɗ'en.
\p 
\v 7 Nga chikawun sǝnkǝ iyawa. Funǝ paaya sǝɗengnandǝhi tǝ tor ɗǝhhacha, la saǝn kandǝfǝwa ɗǝsǝmi la sǝmtǝnda nda i fǝrandǝficha ɗǝhhata. Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn nguchikndǝ kwaakwa'a hur hanndǝkiketa la tǝrkǝndǝwa shiɓndaɗaɗi.
\v 8 Ɗǝsǝmtǝ ɗutǝkǝm nduk tǝ Farǝwa. Ma sǝmwumwa ngǝma tahtǝhiwa, ma shimǝm ngǝma chektǝwa.
\v 9 Kǝ ɗǝfuni indǝsi, mbǝs thlǝt indengnuni mǝ sokiɗa ǝnat chit hansarǝhi mbǝɗa fichile nguchit alchiɗengnandǝsi.
\v 10 Kǝthlǝm ma neɗ yunǝsa le nguchik kwaakwa'a hur fǝrkit, sokǝn tǝ sǝnka sa sǝm'ǝna kǝtǝn mwanandǝ ɗǝhhacha, fǝrauni alchit sǝm i tahsandǝ ficha ɗǝhhachǝwowa?
\v 11 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn hwanmani nguchik kwaakwa'a na sǝndeku sokta mba hǝmtǝ'enhi, le mǝrtǝ Kǝrǝsti ɗi kǝthlǝm mǝlan.
\v 12 Ma shiɗnǝ ɓǝɓichitfat kǝ mbǝɗa hwanmanchiwa, tǝ mbǝnniyu paɗ ɗǝfau ndindita kandǝ kǝ ɗar ɓah kwaakwaa chiɗengnanda, tǝ sǝnǝ ɓǝɓichitfat kǝ mbǝɗa Kǝrǝsti.
\v 13 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn, ma sǝm'ǝn na ɗǝf hwanyaa kǝ yimka hur ɓǝɓichitfata, mwawi tamta chi thlu paɗwa, kǝthlǝm mǝ ɗǝffiɗǝ ndǝ kǝ hǝmǝnhiwa.
\c 9
\s1 Ichi Kamkǝsǝ tǝ Tora Lǝthlǝnda
\p 
\v 1 Njang mbǝs thlǝt indengnǝsǝwowa? Njang nga lǝthlǝndǝ nakiwowa? Anuwi Yǝso Lǝmwaɗengnǝmwowa? Kunang nga kǝni torengnǝ nakuni a hur Lǝmwandǝwowa?
\v 2 Chika sokkǝnwa nga lǝthlǝndǝ naki mbǝɗa funiwa, kittǝkǝn mbǝɗengnuni njang lǝthlǝnda, kǝthlǝm kunang naka sheta tǝ tor lǝthlǝɗengna a hur Lǝmwanda.
\p 
\v 3 Tǝ ndǝkǝn la chandǝ faɗengna kish a mbǝɗa fa tauwasǝnji.
\v 4 Alchiɗengnanisǝ kǝ fǝranguni sǝm'ǝna kani tǝ satwowa?
\v 5 Nga alchiɗengnanisǝ kǝ tǝrani kan kǝ wi'yani tǝ nishchengnani fafǝrkit nda i la sǝt tahhǝt fathlǝncha, tǝ hwanmancha Lǝmwanda tǝ Kefas yuwowa?
\v 6 Nga njang tǝ Barnabas ndak sokkǝ waat kǝ sani tor sǝma'ǝn inchengnani kǝ nanihiwa?
\p 
\v 7 Wun la sǝk tor thlǝrhwata kana sǝma'ǝn indǝ'en? Wun na pat affǝt inabi kǝ cherka chi hwanchikǝn? Wun na hǝrǝm chaɓa kǝ cherka sat yahkǝn?
\v 8 Naki mbu ichiya ɗar yara nifǝwa? Ndu kustǝkǝn kichuwowa?
\v 9 Yarang fichǝhi a hur kussa Musa ndatwa: "Mǝ panǝ hwan sokroka latami mamǝla sǝt tora hurhitǝwa." Lat ndak la hǝrǝmtǝ Farǝwa?
\v 10 Nga shuwunkǝn kǝthlǝm kǝmnangwowa? Aa kǝthlǝm kǝmnang yarandǝ ficha. Kǝthlǝm lǝ huɗata, nakna huɗat tǝ ɗǝffatsǝ nan mbǝs ǝna, le naka ɗǝktǝ paɗ nakna ɗǝktǝ tǝ yarǝ mbǝs'ǝna hur ɗǝsǝmi hitǝkǝn.
\v 11 Ma hifani hanwitǝ shemeɗa Fara hur hanɗǝkikecheng'nuni, kapat ǝnwa ma mbishani icha mbǝɗengnuni?
\v 12 Mana funa mbǝs mba sǝt kichu mbǝɗengnuni, sherawani kandǝ tǝ mba sǝt kichuwowa?
\p Chika kichu suwani tor tǝ mbayiniyuwa, kǝriskani tǝ chikamǝ kǝthlǝm mǝ ɓiɗani tǝ i na njat tor laulawata Kǝrǝstiwa.
\v 13 Sǝnwuniwa fichile la sǝk tora kapat hura'a Fara, la mbǝskǝndǝ ɗǝsǝmtengnanda kapat hura'a Farǝkǝnwowa? Fa sǝt tora bagadi la mbǝskǝndǝ ɗǝsǝmta hur ichi la fǝrtǝ fichi i fǝr pofǝnwowa?
\v 14 Kichuyu paɗ mbutǝ Lǝmwanda ndatwa, fichile naka ɓassǝ laulawata kǝ thlǝndǝ ǝnat nathi engnandǝ tǝ mbǝɗa laulawatkǝn.
\p 
\v 15 Njang tamwi sah ǝn kuni hur ichiniyuwa, paɗ nga naki yarat'iya tǝ ɗǝffatsǝwa kǝ sikǝ fichǝ kichuwa. Kweshkǝn kǝ mǝri, mǝni yuna nji wilwirtengna tǝ ndǝkǝn.
\v 16 Chika kichu ma ɓesshi laulawatkǝn, ngi wilwirtǝwa, kǝthlǝm ɗǝfkǝ fichǝnji waat kǝ ɓassi. Ai engna ma ɓasswi laulawatkǝnwa.
\v 17 Mamuwa la ɓasski a ɗar yahtengna mala kwanikǝ ficha. Sokkǝnwa nga ɗar yahtengnǝwa, tǝni sǝt i malitǝ fichǝhi.
\v 18 Mǝnaka kǝnikǝn engna? Kǝnikǝn engna ndǝkǝn naka ɓasse laulawatkǝn, kǝ ɓassǝ pofǝn. Sǝwitor tǝ cheta mbǝɗengnǝ nat a hur ɓassǝkǝnwa.
\p 
\v 19 Chikama sokkǝn naki kweɗeleng nga hara chikawunwa, saɗi faɗengna mafata nofchǝnat, kǝthlǝm kǝ mbǝsi nofchǝ oi.
\v 20 Kǝ mbǝɗa Yahudawecha, naki nda lǝ Yahudawata, kǝthlǝm kǝ mbǝla'i kahhandǝ hur'incha Yahudawecha. Kǝ mbǝɗa fichile nat kussa alchiɗengnanda, naki nda le naka kakǝn paɗ (chikama sokkǝn njang tǝ indengna nga naki ka kustǝkǝnwa) kǝthlǝm kǝ kahhayi hur'incha fichile naka ka kus tǝkǝn.
\v 21 Fichile nguchika ka kus tǝkǝn sokki nda kandang (chika sokkǝn nga naki kisshitǝ kussa Farǝwa naki ka kussa Kǝrǝsti) kǝthlǝm kǝ kahhayi hur'inda fichile nguchika ka kus.
\v 22 Kǝ mbǝɗa fichile nguchit alchitsi njang ma naki alchitsǝwa, kǝthlǝm kǝ kahhayi hur'incha fichile nguchit alchiɗengnandǝsi. Sokki kǝ ichinat kǝ mbǝɗa nofchǝ nat kǝthlǝm chika tǝ kǝni kǝ hǝrkayi funa.
\v 23 Sǝki ichini natyu kǝthlǝm kusheng shundǝ mbinchin, kǝthlǝm kǝ mbǝsi ǝnhar hur mbǝs'ichihar.
\v 24 Sǝnwuniwa hur fa teri rahta, nat fa teri rahkǝn la kweekǝndǝhi kǝ pǝɗangnda ndanihi, ǝrtǝ ndak la thlǝk kǝnikǝnwowa? Yimamma rahkǝn kǝthlǝm kǝ mbǝsuni kǝnikǝn.
\v 25 Nat fa yimta terriyiniyu, la fǝrangndǝ ɓahta fechengnandǝ chika tǝteni. La sǝkndǝ kichu kǝthlǝm kǝ mbǝsndǝ kǝnikǝn lena sǝɓtaɗi, kǝmnang paɗ la sǝkǝm inǝm kǝ mbǝsǝm kǝnikǝn le nguchika sǝɓtaɗǝ kǝpwaree.
\v 26 A rahwi pofǝn nda nga mbǝt ɗǝtsǝwowa, a tokwi fat nda lela tokkǝ rǝnnawa.
\v 27 Tǝ fǝrayi ɓahta faɗengna kǝ sayi mafata, kǝthlǝm ɗiffitǝ ɓassanda nofchǝsi njang tǝ indengna mǝ nji fichǝ mbǝs kǝnikǝnwa.
\c 10
\s1 Kah Thlǝmat kǝ Ɗar Ɗǝsǝta Isra'ilawecha
\p 
\v 1 Yahkǝsi kǝ sǝnuni, hwanmancha, ndatwa kakechinǝm nat wikǝnda ka husomba'a, paɗ natndǝ ɗǝkndǝ tǝ hur hawurta.
\v 2 A ka husombi'iniyu tǝ hur hawurkǝn sandǝ fichǝ baptisma kandǝ uf kǝ kuwur Musa.
\v 3 Natnda sǝmkǝndǝ ɗǝsǝmta shemeɗa.
\v 4 Natnda sakndǝ ama shemeɗa, kǝthlǝm sheɗndǝ ama a ngwiya shemeɗa le wiikǝ tǝ kanda. Ngwikǝn Kǝrǝsti nakǝn.
\v 5 Chika tǝ kichu, sǝku Farǝ mbǝnfat tǝ funǝ oi a hurnandǝwa, tǝkang fichǝ kandǝhi a loktara.
\p 
\v 6 Sǝk ichininatyu kǝ naka sakchikǝna mbǝɗengnǝm, kǝthlǝm mǝɗi hanndǝkikechengnǝma ɗar ɓǝɓi ichǝ nda i sǝtndǝwa.
\v 7 Mǝ sokiɗuni kǝ fa sǝt tor ɗǝhhachǝ nda i sǝt funengnandǝwa, nda i natna hur yarat laulawatkǝn ndatwa: "Sokkǝ nofchikǝnhi kǝ sǝmndǝ kǝ sanda, thlaakǝnda naknda rǝɓta a hur sǝɓtaɗǝ i fǝlawichita."
\v 8 Mǝ yimindǝma fǝlawichit nda i sǝt funengnandǝwa, ɓaka sǝt nifǝ aru kumchitkum chap tǝ aru kumchit mǝkkan (23,000) mǝrka farǝ ǝrta.
\v 9 Ngǝma kikeɗandǝ Lǝmwandǝwa nda i sǝt funengnandǝwa, ɓak hwithlincha tǝkandǝ kandahi.
\v 10 Mǝ hurmiɗǝm nda i sǝt funengnandǝwa, Mala'ika tǝ ɓǝlta tǝkaǝn kandahi.
\p 
\v 11 Kǝskǝ ichini kandǝyu kǝ naka sakǝtkǝn, yarang fichǝ kandǝhi kǝthlǝm kǝ sǝka ǝnat kah thlǝmaɗengnǝm, kǝmnang ti ɓat ndukwat kisshikǝna mbǝskǝm.
\v 12 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn chikawun yarkǝwa nakǝn kit, kǝ mbǝrǝnsi mǝ hǝmiɗǝhiwa.
\v 13 Kiketǝsi tamka mbǝskuni le mbǝsuchitǝn nifǝwa. Farǝ lǝ kachita, ngu tamta ngǝmtǝ kǝ kikeɗang fichǝ kuni tǝ i na sheranda allengnuniwa. Ma kikeɗa fichǝ kuni nan mbǝssa mba chetakissha kuni, kǝthlǝm kǝ mbǝla'uni kǝrǝskǝn.
\p 
\v 14 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn shikechina, rahamna tor ɗǝhhachihar.
\v 15 Shuwunki tǝ kuni kunang fa hur'incha, kǝ yarangunihi kunang tǝ iɗengnuni i mbuti.
\v 16 Kop i mbǝs'inhar le la sǝtǝm usoko kǝ ɗarkǝn, nga ndǝkǝn la ɗǝfkǝkǝm kǝnǝm ǝrta a hur fwara Kǝrǝstiwowa? Njohmi la chichaɗǝmhi nga ndǝkǝn la ɗǝfkǝkǝm kǝnǝm ǝrta a hur fwara Kǝrǝstiwowa?
\v 17 Kǝthlǝm njohmiya ǝrta, kǝmnang ti nak terchin fat ǝrta, kǝthlǝm nattǝm njohmǝ ǝrtǝ la chiitǝm.
\p 
\v 18 Kǝlamǝn Isra'ilawecha: Fichile la sǝmka hur i fǝrtǝ ficha, nga la humndǝhi tǝ ndani hur sǝm ichi fǝrandǝ ficha Fara a bagadi tǝ fǝr'ichǝwowa?
\v 19 Mǝ nati yarǝ hachiyu? Ɗǝsǝmi fǝrandǝ ficha ɗǝhhacha naka ǝnwa, ndu ɗǝhhakǝn naka ǝna?
\v 20 Auwa, yarengnaa i la fǝrtǝ fa sǝt tor ɗǝhhacha la fǝrangnda lǝwurcha nga Farǝwa. Yahwisǝ kǝ la nuni humtǝhi tǝ lǝwurchǝwa.
\v 21 Nguni sat tǝ kop a Lǝmwandǝ kǝ suni paɗ tǝ i lǝwurchǝwa. Nguni sǝm'ǝna a mbǝt sǝmɗǝsǝmta Lǝmwanda kǝ sǝmuni paɗ a i lǝwurchǝwa.
\v 22 Nǝma ɗǝf Lǝmwandǝ kǝ sǝrǝhtǝwa? Sheraɗǝm tǝ alchitwa?
\s1 Su Chikamǝ Kǝthlǝm Kǝ Mwanangfichǝ Fara
\p 
\v 23 "Nat icha ngǝmaficha kǝmsi", Nga nat ichǝ na kǝsanda kǝmsǝwa. "Nat icha ngǝmaficha kǝmsi." Nga nat ichǝ la tinangwa.
\v 24 Mǝ si nifǝ ǝn ndiichin kǝ ɗar indǝ'en ɗengwa, kǝsǝn kǝ ɗar'inda funǝ paɗ.
\v 25 Chi'u chikawitǝ thlumi, la hi'yandǝ fichaɗa mbǝt hi'yandǝ thluwaɗi, nga tǝ sahmi mbǝɗi ɓat thlukǝnwa, kǝthlǝm mǝni yarengnuni nata mbǝɗi chet thlukǝn.
\v 26 Kǝthlǝm: "Kisshitǝ i Lǝmwanda nat tǝ ichi naka hurkǝn."
\p 
\v 27 Ma eɗ lǝ ɓah fǝrkit sa sǝm ɗǝsǝmta, ngǝmkufǝ ɗǝkuni, sǝmu i ɓandǝ ficha kuni nga tǝ sahmiwa, kǝthlǝm kǝna hur'indǝ ngwalngwal.
\v 28 Ma ndu yunǝwa: "Ɗǝsǝmiya i ɗǝhhata", Mǝ sǝminǝwa, kǝthlǝm le mbukǝ paɗ kǝna hanndǝkiketǝ'en yuyur tǝ sokǝn.
\v 29 Nga yarkiwa hur'iɗekuwa, ikǝn. Yunǝ nan ndatwa kǝthlǝmmǝ nat ficha nji i yahtǝ faɗengna, kǝthlǝm yuyurchit hanndǝkiketa yuna?
\v 30 Ma saɗi Farǝ usoko, kani sǝm ɗǝsǝmkǝn, kǝthlǝmmǝ nat ficha ishnji kǝ ɗar i sandǝ Farǝ usokosi?
\p 
\v 31 Ndu tǝ sǝmna ndu tǝ sana, ndu chika witǝmǝ natu sǝta, su nat kǝthlǝm mwanandǝ thlǝm Fara.
\v 32 Mǝ siɗuni kǝ ǝnat chit hansarǝhiwa, ndu Yahudawecha, ndu fichile nguchika Yahudawecha ndu nofcha Fara.
\v 33 Naki kweetǝhi kǝ tǝrayi hura nofchihi nat chika tǝteni. Nga tǝni kat i na mbǝnanda faɗengnǝfǝwa, paɗ i na mbǝnanda nofchǝfǝ oi, kǝthlǝm kǝ hǝrǝknda.
\c 11
\nb 
\v 1 Sakamnji nda i nati sak Kǝrǝsti.
\s1 I Kamkǝsi kǝ sa Ficha ka Mwanandǝ Fara
\p 
\v 2 Nja hamkuni kǝthlǝm la kuɗukkuni nji chika hurmi, kishshuni ichi sakandǝ kuni har ɗichin nda i fǝrandi kuni.
\p 
\v 3 Yah kisi kǝ sǝnuniwa le naka inn chikawun hishnifa Kǝrǝsti, le naka inn chikawun nuhnifa, hishnifa, le naka inn Kǝrǝsti Fara.
\v 4 Chikawun hishnifǝ hwanka ndu tǝ mbu'ǝn icha Fara indǝ'ena supta, njirtǝ Kǝrǝsti le nak mwanchinna mbanitǝkǝn.
\v 5 Chikawun nuhnifǝ hwanka, ndu tǝ mbu'ǝn icha Fara supwawutǝ i'ndǝwa, njirtǝ sǝmahha le nak mwanchinna mbanitǝkǝn, nakǝn keeke tǝ hǝsandǝ i'ndǝ'enaɗi.
\v 6 Ma cher nuhnifǝ supwandǝ i'ndǝ'en, kǝ hǝsaǝn hwasǝ'enaɗi. Manakǝn harǝfatsi ma hǝsa nuhnifǝ hwasǝ'enaɗi ndu kǝ hǝsangkaɗǝ tukulmur, kǝ supwaǝn.
\v 7 Kamusi hishnifǝ kǝ supwa'ǝn i'ndǝ'enwa, nakǝn kǝ mirshingta paɗ mwanda Fara. Nuhnifa paɗ mwanda hishnifa.
\v 8 Kǝthlǝm a tǝrkakǝn hishnifa nga chekna fata nuhnifǝwa, nuhnifǝ cheka fata hishnifa.
\v 9 Su fichǝ hishnifǝ kǝthlǝm nuhnifǝwa, nuhnifǝ sǝt fichǝ kǝthlǝm hishnifa.
\v 10 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn sokkǝn waat nuhnifǝ kǝ kǝnǝn ɗankwali i'ndǝ'en, che sakǝtkǝna sǝmah nak mwanchin, paɗ kǝthlǝm mala'ikacha.
\v 11 Chika tǝkichu, a hur Lǝmwanda nuhnifǝ nga somǝnhi tǝ hishnifǝwa, hishnifǝ paɗ nga somǝnhi tǝ nuhnifǝwa.
\p 
\v 12 Nda i nat nuhnifǝ chekna fata hishnifa, kichu paɗ nuhnifǝ ngǝtkǝ hishnifa. Ichi nat paɗ ɓaknda mbǝɗa Fara.
\v 13 Yaramǝnhi tǝ inchengnuni, keekesi nuhnifǝ kǝ hwanaǝn Farǝ tǝ indǝ'en chaawa?
\v 14 Sakkawu nathi kǝmharwa ma mel hishnifǝ hwasǝ'en njang, nga ǝnat harǝfata mbǝɗ'enwowa?
\v 15 Ma hwasa nuhnifǝ njang nga mwandǝ'enwa? Fǝrang fichǝ hwasǝ njang kichuyu kǝthlǝm kǝ ngǝlaǝn i'ndǝ'ensi.
\v 16 Ma yunǝsǝ nat halǝ'indǝ'ensi kǝ ɗar iniyu, kanang sǝnwani ɗǝsǝchǝ somǝnwa, nakǝn kichu mbǝɗa tahhǝt nofcha Fara.
\s1 Njirandǝ Sat Jibi Lǝmwandaɗi
\p 
\v 17 Kǝ ichiya hamwi kuniwa, kǝthlǝm ma hwimunihi nga i katkǝnwa i sǝɓkǝn.
\v 18 A tǝrkakǝn, sǝkkiwa ma hwimunihi humta fa tǝrmbanda, a lanak saktǝhisa hurnuni. Ɓeɗi fǝrkita ɗar shuwunkǝn nguɗeh kicha.
\v 19 Sokkǝn waat kǝ mbǝs fichǝ saktǝhi hurnuni, kǝthlǝm kǝ sǝnfichǝ fa kachita hurnuni.
\v 20 Ma hwimunihi nga jibi Lǝmwandǝ la sǝm tuniwa.
\v 21 Kǝthlǝm a chikǝn, chikawun la ɗǝkna mban tǝ sǝm ɗǝsǝmtǝ'en pu'utǝ nifǝwa. Yunǝ tǝ mita fa, yunǝ ngeli har tǝraɗa.
\v 22 Nga hurechengnunisǝ kǝ sǝmuni kǝ suni hurkǝnwowa? Tǝ njiruni fa tǝrmbanda Fara, paɗ kǝnuni ɓahhandǝ fichile nguchit ichengnandǝsi? Mǝnati mbwa'anda kuni? Kǝ hamikuni kǝ iniyuwa? Auwa ngi hamkuniwa.
\p 
\v 23 I fǝrandi kuniya thlǝki mbǝɗa Lǝmwanda ndatwa: Lǝmwandǝ Yǝso, a fiɗiki fǝrtǝ fichǝndi, tǝrkǝn njohma,
\v 24 ɗifitǝ sǝt usoko'en, chichaanhi ndakǝnwa: "Faɗengnǝniya, fǝrtǝ fichǝ kǝthlǝm kunang. La sam kichu kǝthlǝm kuɗuktǝ tǝnji."
\v 25 Mbandǝ ǝrtǝ paɗ, ɗifitǝ jibi tǝkǝn tǝrkǝn kop, ndakǝnwa: "Koptiya i yuwa ɗǝf shundǝhi a hur fwarengna. Sam kichu nat kǝ farǝ natuni sata kǝthlǝm kuɗuktǝ tǝnji."
\v 26 Chika kwat natuni chi njohmiya, paɗ natuni sata a koptiya, nuni mbu mǝrtaɗa Lǝmwanda kǝ fari natna ɓata.
\p 
\v 27 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn, nat le chiikǝ njohmiya, sheɗɗa hur kop ti Lǝmwandǝya nga hur chiɗchiɗchitwa, shiɗtǝ ɓǝɓichitfat kǝ fata tǝ fwara Lǝmwanda.
\v 28 Chikawun kǝ kikeɗaǝn fat'en, kana chi njohhǝmkǝn paɗ kana sata koptǝkǝn.
\v 29 Kǝthlǝm chikawun chiika a sheɗ paɗ ngatǝ mwanandǝ fatkǝna Lǝmwandǝwa, paɗ saɗǝ sakmiya fat'ensi, tǝ mbǝɗa chi'ini tǝ saɗini'enyu.
\v 30 Ndǝkǝn sǝka nofchǝ oi a hurnuni alchiɗengnandǝsǝwa, funǝ haachinnda, paɗ terchina hurnuni a mirnda.
\v 31 Ma yaraɗǝm inchengnǝmhi poo, ngu ficha sakamiya kǝmwa.
\v 32 Ma Lǝmwandǝ sakang miyakǝm, na ficha eltandǝkǝm kǝthlǝm mǝ thlandǝ kita kǝmsǝ tǝ kisshitǝwa.
\p 
\v 33 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn hwanmanchina, ma hwimunihi kǝthlǝm sǝm'ǝna, kǝ pu'uni ndani.
\v 34 Ma yunǝsǝ tǝ mitafa, kǝ sǝmǝn'ǝna huri, kǝthlǝm humtengnuni mǝ ɓandǝ thlet shunda kuniwa.
\p Kǝ ɗar tahhǝt icha, ni mbwa'a mbachǝkǝna kuni ma ɓeɗi.
\c 12
\s1 Fǝr Chiɗchiɗ tǝ Shemeɗ Somsomǝn
\p 
\v 1 Nakǝnya paɗ hwanmancha, pathlǝ fǝr shemeɗ somsomǝn, yahwisǝ kǝnuni tǝ ɓahsǝndǝwa.
\v 2 Shinuniwa fari natuni nga fa tǝrmbandǝwa, limfichǝ kuni paɗ shekɗang fichǝ kuni kǝ fa kuwur ɗǝhhachi nguchit shishingchengnandǝsi.
\v 3 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn yahkǝsi kǝ sǝnuniwa nifǝsǝ na shunda hur Shemeɗa Fara na ndatwa: "Yǝso nga'ǝn nakǝnwa" paɗ nifǝsǝ na ndatwa: "Yǝso Lǝmwandǝ nakǝn." Manga nakna hur Shemeɗ Chiɗchiɗ wa.
\p 
\v 4 Nakǝnya fǝrtǝsǝ somǝn somǝn, Shemeɗ ǝrtǝ la fǝrkǝ kanda.
\v 5 Mbachǝsi somǝn somǝn i sǝt torcha, chika kichu Lǝmwandǝ ǝrta.
\v 6 Torchǝsi somǝn somǝn, chika kichu kǝmka Farǝ ǝrtǝ la fǝrkǝ tori nat chikawuna sǝta.
\p 
\v 7 Chikawuni fǝra Farǝ mba ɓata Shemeɗa kǝthlǝm kǝ kǝsangka chikawunsi.
\v 8 Yuna fǝrang fichǝ Shemeɗ mbǝr shunda, tǝpaɗ yuna Shemeɗ shuwun sǝn'ǝna, natyu tǝ mbǝɗa Shemeɗ ǝrta.
\v 9 Yuna i fǝrkit tǝ mbǝɗa Shemeɗ ǝrta, yuna i kǝnandǝ nofcha ɗi tǝ mbǝɗa Shemeɗini ǝrtǝyu.
\v 10 Yuna fǝrangndǝ alchit sǝt ǝnat pǝɗandǝ nifǝfa, yunǝ i mbu icha Fara le na sǝt kǝmban, yuna i mbǝla sakandǝ shemeɗchǝhi, yuna i sǝn hanshuwunchǝ somǝn somǝn, yunǝ paɗ mbǝla sǝn i nat hanshuwunchi somsomǝnna mbuta.
\v 11 Ichini natyu tora Shemeɗ ǝrtǝ la sǝk kanda, le la sakangnga chikawun nda i yahtǝn.
\s1 Fat Ərta Njarǝchi Somsomǝn
\p 
\v 12 Nda i nat fat ǝrta njarǝchi'en terchin, chikama sokkǝn njarǝchi'en terchin, nakndǝ kǝ fat ǝrta, nak Kǝrǝsti kichuyu.
\v 13 Sangfichi baptisma kǝm nattǝm tǝ Shemeɗ ǝrta kǝ hur fat ǝrta, ndu Yahudawecha, punofcha, ndu mafecha, ndu fichile thlǝk inchengnandaɗi, nattǝm ɗǝfkǝ fichǝkǝm kǝsǝma hur Shemeɗ ǝrta.
\p 
\v 14 Fatkǝn nga tahsang fichǝ tǝ njarǝ ǝrtǝwa, paɗ njarǝchǝkǝn terchin.
\v 15 Mana sara ndatwa: "Njang nga har nakiwa, makichu nga naki fa fatwa." Mbutǝ kichu ngu ɗǝfndǝ kǝ sakndǝhi tǝ njarǝchikǝnna fatkǝnwa.
\v 16 Ma na thlǝmata ndatwa: "Kǝthlǝm njang nga hwanitǝwa, makichu nga naki fa fatwa." Mbutǝ kichu ngu ɗǝfndǝ kǝ sakndǝhi tǝ njarǝchikǝnna fatkǝnwa.
\v 17 Ma fatkǝn nat kǝ hwanita, nakficha la sǝkmbǝt tǝ mi? Ma fatkǝn nat kǝ thlǝmata, nakficha la sa mbǝt tǝ mi?
\v 18 Kittǝkǝn Farǝ tahsang njarǝcha hur fata, chikayeni nda i yahtǝn kǝ nandǝsi.
\v 19 Ma nak fatkǝn nat kǝ njarǝchǝ ǝrta, nak fatkǝna natwa kǝni?
\v 20 Nda i natǝn, njarǝchǝ terchin chika kichu fat ǝrta.
\p 
\v 21 Hwanitǝ ngu ndanda harwa, "Kǝmiwu'ǝntǝsǝwa." Ndu inda kǝ ndangka harchǝwa, "Kǝmiwu'ǝntǝkuniwa."
\v 22 A mbandǝ somǝn, njarǝchi fafat la kǝlandǝ fichǝwa nda nga kwaakwa'a ndǝwa, kandang naka kechikǝn,
\v 23 Njarǝchi fafat la kǝlandǝ fichǝ nda nga ǝnnakndǝwa, kandang la mwanandani kaǝn. Njarǝchi kamuchiksi kǝ nafichiyu, la kǝlak fichasa kanda,
\v 24 njarǝchi'engnǝm nak ndiichinyu, nga ma safichǝ ǝn kandǝwa. Humang Farǝ njarǝcha fata, nda i ngǝrandǝn njarǝchi farawuchit fichi mwanda, sokkǝn tǝ mwanda fa.
\v 25 Sǝkǝn iniyu kǝthlǝm mǝni saktǝhisa hur fatwa, njarǝchikǝn kǝ la tǝrndǝwa nakndǝ nat keeke.
\v 26 Ma njarǝsǝ ǝrtǝ naka ɓahta, nat ndǝ nanda nata hur ɓahta, ma njarǝsǝ ǝrtǝ fǝrandǝ fichǝ mwanda, nat njarǝchikǝn kǝ mbǝnndǝ fata.
\p 
\v 27 Nakǝnya kunang naka fata Kǝrǝsti, chikawun ǝrta hurnuni nakǝn kǝ njarǝchi'en.
\v 28 A kǝtǝn mwanandǝ Fara hertǝ nofchǝhar, saǝn funa tǝrkakǝn kǝ Fathlǝncha, chapatǝkǝn Tapǝnecha, mǝkkatǝkǝn fa sakaɗaɗi, funǝ fa sǝt ǝnat pǝɗandǝ nifǝfa, funǝ fa kǝnandǝ nofchaɗi, funǝ fa kǝsanda nofchǝsi, funǝ fa kǝlandǝ tora nofcha paɗ funǝ fa shundǝ tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝn.
\v 29 Nat fatǝrmbakǝn fathlǝnchǝwa? Nat fatǝrmbakǝn tapǝnechǝwa? Nat fatǝrmbakǝn fa sakandaɗaɗiwa? Nat fatǝrmbakǝn fa sǝt ǝnat pǝɗandǝ nofchǝfǝwa?
\v 30 Nat fatǝrmbakǝn fa mbǝs fǝr kǝnandǝ nofchandǝwa? Nat fatǝrmbakǝn fa shundǝ tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝnwa? Nat fatǝrmbakǝn fa mbu sakǝt i shuwuntǝ fichǝ tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝnwa?
\v 31 Paɗ kam fǝrtǝ somsomǝn tǝ rahta fichile nak ka mwanchin.
\p Ni cheɗa mbanda kuni le sherkǝ nat tǝ ndata.
\c 13
\s1 Mba Mbǝnfata
\p 
\v 1 Chikama la mbǝrki shundǝ tǝ hanshuwuncha nofcha tǝ i Mala'ikacha, nakǝn mbǝnfatsa faɗengniwa, sokki nda pupwandǝra lǝ la tik kaǝn, manga kichuwa nda thlǝmra.
\v 2 Chikama fǝrtengnǝsi i mbu'icha Fara paɗ la mbǝsayi ichi ɓuɓweeta tǝ sǝndǝ nat, ma fǝrkitchiɗengnǝsǝ kaǝn ni mbǝla mbasandǝ shohlachaɗi nga mbǝnfatsa faɗengniwa nga ǝn nakiwa.
\v 3 Chikama ni fǝra ichi naksengnǝ nata fa ɓahcha kǝ fǝri faɗengna kǝ 'yangfichaɗi manga mbǝnfatsa faɗengniwa, ǝnsǝ nati mbǝstisǝwa.
\p 
\v 4 Mbǝnfata kǝrǝstǝ'ensi, tǝ kafata, sǝrǝhtǝsa hur mbǝnfatwa, thla'andǝ'ensǝwa, mwa'indǝsǝwa.
\v 5 Mbǝnfata thla'indǝsǝwa, yah'indǝsa hur mbǝnfatwa, sǝɓhursǝ paapawa, kǝs'ǝnsahurwa.
\v 6 Mbǝnfata yahutǝ sǝɓfatwa, la mbǝnkǝnfat kǝ i sǝtficha ɗar kit.
\v 7 Mbǝnfat la nakǝn tǝ kǝrǝstafa kǝɗing chika hur witǝmi, la nakǝn tǝ fǝrkit hur chikamǝ nat, la ɗǝfkǝn hanndǝkiketa ichinat, la kǝrǝskǝn tǝ ichinat.
\p 
\v 8 Tamu mbǝnfata tuɓwatwa kǝparee. Mbu'ichi Farǝ na sǝt kǝmban nan thlǝrǝttaɗi, shundǝ tǝ hanshuwunchi somsomǝn nan shekata, sǝn'ǝna nan thlǝrǝttaɗi.
\v 9 Sǝn'ǝnengnǝm nǝhɗuhiwa. Mbu'ichi chandǝ Fara kish ngǝ mbǝɗengnǝm nǝhɗuhiwa.
\v 10 Ma ɓeɗ le nǝhhǝɗkǝhi, le nǝhɗuchikhi nan thlǝrǝttaɗi.
\v 11 Thlahmbǝɗi nati kǝ hweya, la shuwunkǝ nda hweya, la yarki nda hweya, la mbuki ichi kamkǝsi nda hweya. Kǝ sǝkti nifa, malayi hwanchita.
\v 12 Nakǝnya la nakǝm nda a hur shishing'ama, shummǝ shumma, farǝkǝn nakma nat hwanitǝ tǝ hwanita. Sǝn'ǝnengna nakǝnya nǝhɗuhiwa, a farǝkǝn na sǝɗengna nǝhhatǝhi nda i sǝntǝfichinji ndiichin.
\p 
\v 13 Nakǝnya, ichi mǝkkanya shokndǝ kichu, fǝrkit, ɗǝf hanndǝkiketǝsi, tǝ mbǝnfata. Le nak mwanchina hurnanda mbǝnfata.
\c 14
\s1 Fǝr Hanshuwunchǝ Somsomǝn // tǝ Mbu'ichi Naka Yara Fara
\p 
\v 1 Kwe'yamhi kǝ kuni mbǝnfata, kǝ kuni fǝrta Shemeɗ Chiɗchiɗ, nda i yah mbu ichi naka yara Fara.
\v 2 Kǝthlǝm le la shuwunkǝ tǝ hanshundǝ somǝn, nga tǝ nofchǝ natna shundǝwa tǝ Fara, nifǝsǝ la sǝnkǝ i natna mbutǝwa, la mbukǝn icha ɓuɓweeta mbǝɗa alchita Shemeɗa.
\v 3 Le la mbukǝ ichi na yara Fara, na shunandǝ nofcha kǝ tinaǝn kanda, kǝ chekaǝn alchita kanda, kǝ saǝn sǝssi kanda.
\v 4 Le naka shundǝ tǝ hanshundǝ somǝn naka tinaɗǝ fat'en, paɗ le naka mbu'ichi na yara Fara tinaɗǝ fatǝrmbanda.
\v 5 Yahkisi natuni kǝ shununi tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝn, ɓureɗi yahtǝ kǝ mbu'uni ichi na yara Fara. Le la mbukǝ ichi na yara Fara, sheraɗa le la shuwunkǝ tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝn, ma mbwi yunǝ hanngalǝ i mbutǝn, kana tinandǝ fatǝrmbanda.
\p 
\v 6 Nakǝnya hwanmancha, ma ɓeɗi mbǝskuni nja shundǝ tǝ hanshuwuncha, mǝ natna chekanda kuni ma mbwa'awi hangngalǝ shuwunkǝna kuniwa, ndu sǝnda, ndu ichi na yara Fara, ndu sakandaɗi?
\v 7 Nakǝn kichu tǝ ichi nguchit shishingtǝsa fechengnanda, nda kǝla'a tǝ ǝnat pecha, ma chu ɓurechengnanda kish ɗiichinwa, wun na sǝn i nat ficha futa tǝ i nat ficha peta?
\v 8 Ma pyawu fichǝ kutmetǝ keeke tǝ i nat ficha sǝndǝwa, wun na sǝhatǝfǝ kǝ mbata?
\v 9 Nakǝn kichu mbǝɗengnuni, ma shununi tǝ hanshuni mbǝsauchit ficha, nakficha sǝn i mbutuniwa kǝni? Shuwunkuniyu mere pǝɗakna hur rǝnna'a.
\v 10 Michisi somsomǝna hur kisshita, chika yen miya tǝ sakǝtkǝnsi.
\v 11 Ma sǝnwi sakǝt mikǝnwa, naki nat kǝ roma mbǝɗa lǝ shuwunkǝn, lǝ shuwunkǝn paɗ nakǝn kǝ roma mbǝɗengna.
\v 12 Nakǝn kichu mbǝɗengnuni, nakuni tǝ ɓwechit hura a ɗar mbǝs fǝr Shemeɗchi somsomǝn, fǝram alchiɗengnuni kǝ suni tor tǝ fǝr Shemeɗǝ na tinandǝ fatǝrmbanda.
\p 
\v 13 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn, chikawun na shundǝ tǝ hanshundǝ somsomǝn kǝ hwanǝn kǝ fǝrang fichǝ mba sǝn i mbutǝn.
\v 14 Kǝthlǝm ma hweni tǝ hanshundǝ somǝn, shemeɗengnǝ hwanka, paɗ yarengnǝ cheku tǝ ǝnwa.
\v 15 Mǝnati sǝta? Ni hwandǝ tǝ shemeɗengna, ni hwandǝ tǝ yarengnǝ paɗ. Ni ǝn'imshi tǝ shemeɗengna, ni i'ndǝ tǝ yarengnǝ paɗ.
\v 16 Manga kichuuwa, masa sǝt usoko tǝ shemeɗeku, tǝ kǝni le naka kuthlǝmata mbǝsauchik hanshuniniyu ndatwa: "Kǝ sokǝn kichu wa kǝnǝ." Kǝ ɗar usoko tǝ natu sǝta, ma sǝnutǝ i natu mbutǝwa?
\v 17 Chika sokkǝnwa shiɗi usoko kaǝn, ǝnsǝ chekandǝna le nak nduk tǝsǝ le sǝnuchikwa.
\p 
\v 18 Saɗi Farǝ usoko sheraɗi kuni tǝ shundǝ tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝn.
\v 19 Chika kichu, a hur kǝtǝn hwanda kweshikǝn kǝ mbu'i ichi ɗurman tǝ hanndǝkiketengna kǝthlǝm kǝ sakayi funǝhar mǝni mbu ichi aru kumchitkum (10,000) tǝ hanshundǝ somsomǝn.
\p 
\v 20 Hwanmancha, malamǝn yarǝ'ichǝ nda hwecha. Kǝnuni hwecha a hur ɓǝɓichitfata, kǝnuni pǝktecha hur yarengnuni.
\p 
\v 21 A hur kus yara fichǝhiwa:
\q1 "Tǝ mbǝɗa nofcha fa hanshuwunchǝ
\q2 somsomǝn paɗ tǝ miya
\q1 romcha nati shundǝ tǝ nofchiya,
\q2 chika tǝkichu ngunda kithlǝmatwa,
\q1 ndat Lǝmwanda."
\p 
\v 22 Awi shundǝ tǝ hanshuwuncha nakndǝ kǝ sakǝtkǝn nga kǝ mbǝɗa fa fǝrkitwa kǝ mbǝɗa fa ɓahfǝrkit. Mbu yara Fara i fafǝrkit nga i fa ɓahfǝrkitwa.
\v 23 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn ma hwim fatǝrmbandǝhi, kana chikawunna nata shundǝ tǝ hanshuwunchi somsomǝn, nakǝn funǝsǝ mbǝsaundǝ i nat ficha sǝtwa, ndu funǝ fa ɓahfǝrkit yimkǝsi, ngunda ndatwa nga nakuni hur'inchǝwa?
\v 24 Ma chikawuna mbu yari Farǝ na sǝtta, kana lǝ ɓahfǝrkit ndu yunǝ roma yimtǝsi le sǝnuchik i nat ficha sǝtta, ɓak shunda chikawuna tǝka harfa a kakǝn tǝrtǝhi.
\v 25 Naficha chaɗǝ ɓuɓwee ichi kissha hanɗǝkiketǝ'enyu, tǝ kichu hǝmkǝnhi mwanaǝn Fara ndakǝnwa: "Kittǝkǝn Fara hurnuni."
\s1 Kǝ Mwanang Fichǝ Fara Mbayi Kamkǝsi
\p 
\v 26 Mǝ natma mbuta hwanmancha? Ma hwimunihi yuna imshǝ'ensi i mwanandǝ Fara, yunǝ sakandaɗi, yunǝ mbu'icha, yunǝ shundǝ tǝ hanshundǝ somsomǝn, yuna fǝr hanngalǝ shunda. Sam ichǝnat kǝthlǝm tinandǝ fafǝrkit.
\v 27 Mana yuna shundǝ tǝ hanshundǝ somsomǝn, mǝ sheraɗa nifǝ chap ndu mǝkkanwa, kǝ sǝndǝ ɗeɗerra paɗ yunǝ kǝ fǝrǝn hanngalǝ shuwunkǝn.
\v 28 Manga yunǝsǝ na fǝr hanngalǝ shuwunkǝnwa, chikawun kǝ ngasǝn ɓa'a hur fatǝrmbakǝn, kǝ shunaǝn fat'en tǝ Fara.
\p 
\v 29 Tapǝnechǝ chap ndu mǝkkan kǝ shuwunnda, tahchikǝn kǝ kikeɗangndǝ hǝɓakkǝ i mbutǝnda.
\v 30 Ma yunǝsa mbǝnniyu ɗas ɓat sǝn'ichikǝna mbǝt'en, le naka shunda tǝrkakǝnyu kǝ ngasǝn ɓa.
\v 31 Natuni nuni mbǝla mbu ichi na yara Fara ǝrtǝ ǝrta, kǝthlǝm kǝ sak chikawuni paɗ kǝ mbǝs chikawun alchita,
\v 32 Tapǝnecha la mbǝllakǝndǝ hǝrǝm inchengnandǝ har.
\v 33 Fara nga Farǝ la shekɗandǝ i'ndǝwa, i yuyurchita.
\p Nakǝn kichu mbǝɗa fatǝrmbaɗǝ chiɗchiɗ,
\v 34 kǝ ngas nishchǝ ɓa a hur kǝtǝn hwacha. Kǝthlǝm fǝrau fichǝ mbanda kandǝ kǝ shuwunndǝwa, kǝ kuwurndǝ ndak nda i mbutǝ kus.
\v 35 Ma ǝnsǝ yahtǝnda sahta, kǝ sahhangndǝ hishchǝngnanda huri. Kǝthlǝm ǝnat harǝfata kǝ shuwun nuhnifa a hur kǝtǝn hwanda.
\p 
\v 36 Tǝrkaakǝ shunda Fara ɓat tǝ mbǝɗengnuniwa, ndu kunang ndak sa'andǝn?
\v 37 Mala yarkǝ yunǝwa tapǝnaa nakǝn, ndu le mbǝskǝ fǝrta shemeɗa, kǝ sǝnǝnwa ichi nati yaranda kunisǝya mbuta Lǝmwanda.
\v 38 Ma cher yunǝ mbǝnnifiyu, mǝlan ma kǝ cherunindǝfa.
\p 
\v 39 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn hwanmancha, namtǝ ɓweechit hur mbu ichi na yara Fara paɗ mǝ malaɗuni shundǝ tǝ hanshuwunchǝ somsomǝnwa.
\v 40 Kǝ suni chikama a mbayi kamkǝsi, paɗ a hur tahhasǝkǝn.
\c 15
\s1 Thlata Kǝrǝsti Hur Mǝmatcha
\p 
\v 1 Nakǝnya, hwanmancha, ni kuɗkanda kuni kwescha shuni ɓassandi kuniyu, le thlǝtuni thlartuni ɗarkǝn.
\v 2 Tǝ mbǝɗa kwescha shuwunkǝn hǝrǝktuni, ma kisshuni shunihar mbwa'andǝ kuni kwaakwaa. Manga kichuuwa fǝrkit engnuni mere.
\p 
\v 3 I kamkǝsi sǝnandi kunisi, ndǝkǝn naka i thlǝta, ndatwa: "Kǝrǝsti mǝrkǝnaɗi kǝthlǝm ɓǝɓichitfechengnǝm, nda i natna hur yarat laulawata Farǝ le mbutǝn,
\v 4 ndatwa thloha ficha, farǝ mun mǝkkatǝkǝn thla'aficha, nda i natna hur yarat laulawatkǝn,
\v 5 cheɗaɗǝ fat'ena Kefas kana fichile kumngǝrǝnsǝ chapyu.
\v 6 Kana cheɗa fat'ena hwanmancha fichile sheranga aru ɗurman (500) a farǝ ǝrta, mweefunǝsi tǝ shisshingtafa, chikama sokkǝn funa mirnda.
\v 7 Kana cheɗa fat'ena Yakubu, tǝ tahhǝt fathlǝnchǝkǝn nat.
\v 8 A mweshitkǝn nat, cheɗikǝn fata, nda le ngǝttǝ ficha a fari kamuchiksǝ.
\p 
\v 9 Kǝthlǝm njang naka mweshitmiya fathlǝncha, kamuchiksǝ kǝ afichǝwa lǝthlǝnda, kǝthlǝm fǝraɗi ɓahta fa tǝrmbanda Fara.
\v 10 Tǝ mbǝɗa kafata Fara nati kǝ i natiya, kafat'en kǝ mbǝɗengna nga merewa. Shiɗi tor sheraɗi chikawuna hurnanda, chikama sokkǝn nga njangwa, kafaɗi Farǝ nak tǝ njiyu.
\v 11 Ndu njang ndu kaɗang, ɓasskani kichuyu, tǝ kichuyu paɗ fǝrtuni kit.
\s1 Thlata Mǝmatcha
\p 
\v 12 Ma ficha ɓassǝ thlata Kǝrǝsti a hur mǝmatcha, mǝsǝk la ndat funengnuniwa thlata mǝmatchǝsǝwa?
\v 13 Ma nga thlata mǝmatchǝsǝwa, sokkǝn chika Kǝrǝsti thla'awu fichǝwa.
\v 14 Ma thlaawu fichǝ Kǝrǝstiwa, ɓassengnani pofǝn, fǝrkitchiɗengnuni pofǝn.
\v 15 Ma tana nakǝn kichu, shiɗani fa lekta Fara, kǝthlǝm shiɗani sheta kǝ ɗar Farǝwa thla'aɗǝ Kǝrǝsti hur mǝmatcha, le thla'awuchitǝn, ma tǝ kitwa thla'awu fichǝ mǝmatchǝwa.
\v 16 Kǝthlǝm ma thla'awu fichǝ mǝmatchǝwa, sokkǝn Kǝrǝsti ma thla'awu fichǝwa.
\v 17 Ma sokkǝn thla'awu fichǝ Kǝrǝstiwa, fǝrkitchiɗengnuni pofǝn paɗ paaya mwakuni hur ɓǝɓichitfechengnuni.
\v 18 Sokkǝn fichile fǝrkǝkitta hur Kǝrǝsti, kannda mǝrtaɗi thlǝrǝtkǝndaɗi.
\v 19 Ma ɗǝfǝm hanɗǝkiketengnǝm kǝ Kǝrǝsti kǝthlǝm naɗihiya ɗeng, sheraɗima chikawun kǝ ǝnat haɗandǝ nifǝfa.
\p 
\v 20 Kitchitkǝn thla'afichǝ Kǝrǝsti a hur mǝmatcha, mǝlan naka tǝrka thlata fichile mǝrkaɗi.
\v 21 Nakǝn ɓak murtǝ tǝ mbǝɗa nifa ǝrta, tǝ mbǝɗa nifǝ ǝrta paɗ ɓat thlata mǝmatcha.
\v 22 Nda i nat ficha mǝmattǝ kǝthlǝm Adamu, kichu paɗ kǝthlǝm Kǝrǝsti nat ficha thla'andǝ nofchǝ nat.
\v 23 Nak thlakǝna nata ndera chikawun tǝ witǝ ikǝn, Kǝrǝsti na nata tǝrkakǝn, kana fichile naka ikǝn a fari natna ngǝrandǝ'in.
\v 24 Kana mweshitmikǝna ɓata, fari natna fǝra kuturǝchita Fara Shinda, ɗifitǝ wuwwelandǝ fa kuturǝchitaɗi, nat tǝ kuturcha tǝ alchita.
\v 25 Waat nan sok kuturǝchita, kana ɗǝf atikrechikǝn kǝ ka sarǝchi'en.
\v 26 Hanmurtǝ naka mweshitmi atikretǝkǝn ti natna ɓǝllanda.
\v 27 "Kǝthlǝm shiɗtǝ ichinat kǝ ka sarǝchi'en" Ma ɗeɗfichǝwa: "Shiɗtǝ ichinat kǝ ka sarǝchi'en", cheɗakissha ɗwaachitkǝnwa nga nat tǝ Farǝ tǝ indǝ'enwa, le ɗǝfkǝ chikamǝnat kǝ ka Kǝrǝsti.
\v 28 Kǝ ngǝrandǝ Farǝ ichiniyu kǝ ka sarǝchi'en, hwankǝn paɗ sokkǝna ka Fara, kana Fara nata chikamǝ tǝ tǝmǝ nat.
\p 
\v 29 Manga thlata mǝmatchǝsǝwa, mǝnat nofchiya sǝta, fichile sandǝ fichǝ baptisma kanda kǝthlǝm mǝmatcha? Ma thla'awu fichǝ mǝmatchǝwa kǝpware, kǝthlǝmmǝ la sandǝ fichǝ baptisma nofchǝ kǝthlǝm kandang?
\v 30 Kǝthlǝmmǝ la natma ɗǝf inchengnǝma hur mboro chikayen hanthlǝkta?
\v 31 Wembǝta nja miya hanmurta! Yarkiyaa hwanmancha, kittǝkǝn la thla'ayi'indǝ kǝthlǝm kunang hur Yǝso Kǝrǝsti Lǝmwaɗengnǝm.
\v 32 Ma mbeɗi tǝ pǝktat hanthlucha a Afisa, kǝthlǝm yarengnǝ kǝ ɗar nifa, mǝ naka mbǝstengnǝhar? Mangu ficha thla'andǝ mǝmatchǝwa,
\q1 "Nga kwesh kǝ sǝmǝm kǝ sǝmwa nakǝn ishki nǝma mǝrta?"
\m 
\v 33 Mǝ lǝmi fichǝ kuniwa: "Soktǝ tǝ ɓǝɓinofcha la sǝɓaǝn ka hur'indaɗi."
\v 34 Ɓamaɗi kǝ hur'inchengnuni ndiichin, kǝ malanguni sǝt ɓǝɓichitfata. Kǝthlǝm funengnuni sǝnundǝ Farǝwa. Mbuki iniyu kǝthlǝm kǝ harangfat kuni.
\s1 Thlata Fata
\p 
\v 35 Paɗ funǝ nanda sahtǝ ndatwa: "La thla'ang fichǝ mǝmatchǝwa kǝni? Tǝ witǝ fatmǝ natnda ɓata?"
\v 36 Ɓoma! I hǝftu ngu tiftǝwa se ma mirwa.
\v 37 Ma hifna, nga cheta i hǝftu tǝ fatkǝn na tiftǝwa, hanwitǝkǝn ndak. Ndu i alkama ndu hanwitǝ ǝn somǝn.
\v 38 Farǝ la fǝrang fata hanwitǝkǝn nda i yahtǝn, paɗ chika witǝ hanwitǝmi la fǝraǝn fatkǝn'en.
\v 39 Nga nat thlu ǝrtǝwa, nofchǝ tǝ witǝ thlǝwengnanda ǝrta, ɗǝhǝrǝmchǝ tǝ witǝ innanda, ɗishchǝ tǝ witǝ innanda, tinchǝ paɗ tǝ witǝ innanda.
\v 40 Tinɗǝsi i afshi neɗsǝ paɗ i kisshita, mwanda i afshi somǝn, mwanda i kisshitǝ paɗ somǝn.
\v 41 Mwanda hwatfarǝ somǝn, i ndǝraa somǝn, i hanndǝrechǝ somǝn; kǝthlǝm yunǝ hanndǝraa somǝn mwandǝ'en tǝ le.
\v 42 Nakǝn kichu tǝ pathlǝ thlata mǝmatcha. I hǝftǝ ficha nan yirataɗi, i thla'andǝ ficha yirat'ensaɗǝwa.
\v 43 La hǝfkǝ ficha tǝ ɓah fǝr mwanda, thla'ang ficha hur mwanda. La hǝfkǝ ficha hur ɓah alchita, thla'ang ficha hur alchita.
\v 44 Hǝfkǝ ficha hur cheta fata, thla'ang ficha hur fata shemeɗa. Nakǝn fatsǝ i cheta fata, fatsǝ paɗ i shemeɗa.
\p 
\v 45 Nakǝn kichu hur yaratkǝn, "Adamu tǝrka nifa sokka nifǝ tǝ shisshingtafa, ndukwalat Adamu shemeɗa lela fǝrkǝ shisshingta.
\v 46 Nga le naka i shemeɗ naka tǝrkakǝnwa, i punifǝchita, kana i shemeɗa.
\v 47 Tǝrka nifa chekna hur furta a hur kisshita, chapatǝ nifa ɓakna hur afshi
\v 48 Nda ini chet nifa hur furtuyu, nakǝn kichuyu tǝ fichile naka i furta. Nda i'ni nat leni hur afshiyu, kichu paɗ natna nata kǝ fichile naka i hur afshi.
\v 49 Nda i'ni tǝrtǝm mirshingta leni cheka hur furtuyu, kichu paɗ natma tǝr mirshingta le naka hur afshi.
\p 
\v 50 I nati mbwa'anda kuni, hwanmancha, ngusǝtta faɗengnǝm nda thlu tǝ fwara kǝ yimnda kuturǝchita Farǝwa. Kichu paɗ lǝ yirata ngu mbǝs ǝna a ratǝ le nguchika yiratwa.
\v 51 Kamthlǝmathi, ni mbwa'a ǝna kuni ɓuɓweeta. Ngǝma mǝrtǝ natǝmwa, natǝm naficha ɓuɓweɗandǝkǝmhi,
\v 52 Nda nakǝnya a tǝɓǝrta hwanitǝhi, a mweshitmi kutmeta. Naficha pyandǝ kutmeta, thla'ang fichǝ mǝmatcha tǝ faɗi nguchika yirata, kana ficha ɓuɓweɗandǝ kǝmhi.
\v 53 Kǝthlǝm faɗi na yirata waat kǝ ɓuɓweɗang fichǝhi tǝle nguchika yirata, lela mǝrkǝ paɗ kǝ ɓuɓweɗang fichǝ tǝle nguchika mǝrta.
\v 54 Le na yirata ma ɓuɓweɗa fichǝhi tǝle nguchika yirata, le na mǝrta kǝ ɓuɓweɗang fichǝ tǝle nguchika mǝrta, a mbǝnniyu nat i yarandǝ fichǝhi hur shunda Farǝ nan nǝhhatǝhi ndatwa:
\q1 "Mǝhɗafichǝ hanmurta, shera ficha al'en."
\v 55 "Ai hanmurta, mbǝs'ǝnekuhara ayi? Ai hanmurta, alchiɗeku ayi?"
\p 
\v 56 Alchita hanmurta ɓǝɓichitfata, kus naka alchita ɓǝɓichitfata.
\v 57 Usoko Fara le fǝrang mbǝs'ǝna kǝmhar tǝ mbǝɗa Lǝmwaɗengnǝm Yǝso Kǝrǝsti.
\v 58 Kǝthlǝm ndǝkǝn hwanmanchinǝ ti yahti, thlaramhi kit, mǝ fohha ǝnkuniɗiwa. Kǝnding kǝ fǝrunǝ fechengnuni nat kǝ tora Lǝmwanda, kǝthlǝm shinuniwa ɓahtengnunihi hur Lǝmwanda ngu nat pofǝnwa.
\c 16
\s1 Kǝsanda Fichilesǝ Nak Chiɗchiɗ
\p 
\v 1 Nakǝnya pathlǝ kǝsaanda fichilesǝ nak chiɗchiɗ, sam nda i ndaɗi mbǝt ngǝlhwanichi a Galatiyayu.
\v 2 A farǝ ladi, tǝrka chika yen mundǝ muɗ, chikawuni kǝla ɗǝfǝn hanndǝɓǝltǝhi kǝlar hur i la mbǝlaatǝn mbǝsta kǝ kǝsǝnhar, kǝthlǝm ma ɓeɗi mǝni hum'icha natsǝwa.
\v 3 Ma she'i ni thlǝn fichile hartunihar, ngǝmtuni tǝkanda, tǝ yarat ɗelwer kǝ ɗǝndǝ tǝ fǝrpofǝn engnuni kǝ Urshelima.
\v 4 Ma sokkǝnwa keekesi njang paɗ kǝ ɗi, natnda ɗǝfkǝɗǝnji.
\s1 Tahhasǝfǝ i Wita
\p 
\v 5 Ni ɓata mbǝɗengnuni ma ɗiɗi tǝ Makidoniya, kǝthlǝm yahkisi kǝ ɗi tǝ Makidoniya.
\v 6 Mbah kǝ si tolla mbǝɗengnuni, mbahya ma kǝ mbǝrayi fektǝhi mbǝnniyu, kǝthlǝm kǝ kǝsikunisi nat mbǝɗi nati ɗǝta.
\v 7 Nga yahtengna kǝnikuni nakǝnya kǝ mbǝrihi ndakwa, ɗǝfi hanndǝkiketǝsi kǝ muni tolla mbǝɗengnuni, ma ngǝma Lǝmwandǝ.
\v 8 Paɗ ni thlarǝhi a Afisa kǝ farǝ Pentekos,
\v 9 Kǝthlǝm i'ni fichǝ mikǝnndǝsǝ hauyang i tor nat tǝ mbǝs'ǝnsi chika sokkǝn atikrechisǝ kaǝn.
\p 
\v 10 Ma ɓeɗ Timoti, kǝ ngǝmangnguni kǝ kalǝn fathi hurnuni, kǝthlǝm mǝlan ma na sǝt tora Lǝmwandǝ nda i nati sǝtta.
\v 11 Mǝ cherinduni thlǝtndǝwa, kǝ kǝsangngunisa hur witǝ'en yuyur, kǝthlǝm kǝ ngǝraǝn i'na mbǝɗengna, nja kǝlata mba ɓat'en tǝ hwanmancha.
\p 
\v 12 Nakǝnya pathlǝ hwanmanǝm Afolos paɗ, hwanaɗi tǝ alchitafa kǝ ɗǝka mbǝɗengnuni tǝ tahhǝt hwanmancha, nakǝn nga yahtǝ'en kǝ ɗǝn nakǝnyawa. Nan ɗǝta ma mbish tǝ mbanda.
\s1 Mweshit Mi Shunda
\p 
\v 13 Sokam tǝ tahhasǝfa, kǝ thlaruni kit tǝ alchita a hur fǝrkitengnuni, kǝnuni nda hishcha, kǝnuni tǝ alchitafa.
\v 14 I natuni sǝtnat kǝ suni hur mbǝnfata.
\v 15 Hwanmancha, shinuni nofchi hura'a Istifanus kanda tǝrkakǝ tǝrtǝhi a hur hachahai Akaya, paɗ firndǝ fechengnanda kǝ sangndǝ tora fichile nak chiɗchiɗ.
\v 16 Nja hwanandǝ kuni kǝ fǝranguni mwanda witǝ nofchiniyu, tǝ fichile naka shikechǝ torchengnani tǝ ɓahtengnani.
\v 17 Shiki mbǝndǝfǝ tǝ ɓata Istifanus, tǝ Fartunatus, tǝ Akaikus, le sokkǝ nda kunang ɓaka.
\v 18 Tǝrandǝ hurengnǝhi nat tǝ innuni. Witǝ nofchiniyu kǝla fǝranguni mwanda kanda.
\s1 Mweshitmi Ndat'icha
\p 
\v 19 Fa tǝrmbayi Asiyayu kanda nda'icha kuni. Akila tǝ Biriskila tǝ fa tǝrmbayi la humkǝhi hure'engnandǝyu, kanda nda'icha kuni kaǝn hur thlǝm Lǝmwanda.
\v 20 Hwanmanchi natta mbǝnniyu kanda nda'ǝna kuni. Kǝ ndangnguni icha ndani tǝ chiɗchiɗ tǝ kǝsndanihar.
\v 21 Njang Bulus yarak ndat'ǝnaɗiya tǝ harengna.
\v 22 Ma yunǝsǝ nguchit mbǝnfat'ensi kǝ mbǝɗa Lǝmwanda, kǝnaka sǝɓkǝn. Lǝ Lǝmwada a ɓu.
\v 23 Kafata Lǝmwandǝ Yǝso kǝnan tǝ kuni.
\v 24 Malan mbǝnfaɗengna kǝnan tǝ kuni natuni hur Yǝso Kǝrǝsti. Kǝsokǝn kichu.
